tc.research_name.RESEARCH=研究
tc.research_text.RESEARCH=如何发现物品
tc.research_page.RESEARCH.1=Before you can build most thaumaturgical items and blocks, you first need to discover how to do so. This can be done in two ways:<BR>(1) Using the aspects you know and discovering practical knowledge and recipes with the §5Research Table§0.<BR><BR>(2) Exploring the world and examining blocks, items and creatures with a §5Thaumometer§0 in order to gain clues to further research<LINE>Before you can do either of these you will have to craft a §5Thaumometer§0 and a research table.
tc.research_page.RESEARCH.2=To craft a §5Research Table§0 simply place a wooden table in the world and click on it with scribing tools.<BR>The recipes for the §5Thaumometer§0 and §5Scribing Tools§0 will be shown later.<LINE><IMG>thaumcraft:textures/research/research1.png:0:0:255:208:.5</IMG>
tc.research_page.RESEARCH.3=§l§n(1) Primary Research§r<BR>You need to be carrying a set of scribing tools and paper for this step. If you open your Thaumonomicon you will see all the knowledge you already have and also all the knowledge that you are now able to pursue.<IMG>thaumcraft:textures/research/research2.png:0:0:128:83:1</IMG> 
tc.research_page.RESEARCH.4=Flashing square or round icons represent primary researches you can pursue.<BR>When you click on one of these flashing icons paper and ink will be consumed from your inventory and you will gain a research note.<BR>You can now take this research note to the table to start researching it by placing scribing tools in slot §l1§r (which should happen automatically when you create the table) and the research note in slot §l2§r.
tc.research_page.RESEARCH.5=Section §l3§r will show a number of primal aspects that you have available to you to complete the research.<BR>Section §l5§r will now display a sheet of paper covered in hexagonal tiles with aspect icons around the outer edge.<IMG>thaumcraft:textures/research/research2.png:0:88:255:158:.5</IMG>
tc.research_page.RESEARCH.6=To complete your research you simply need to connect and activate all the aspects. You do this by dragging an aspect to a hex adjacent to it that is either composed of the target aspect, or can be combined with another aspect to form the target aspect.<IMG>thaumcraft:textures/research/research3.png:0:0:150:95:.75</IMG>
tc.research_page.RESEARCH.7=Placing an aspect consumes one research point. If you make a mistake you can click on the aspect to remove it, but you will not regain the research point.<BR>Should you ever run out of research points it is best to discard the note and create a new one to get a fresh pool of research points.<BR>To get the compound aspects required to complete most researches you will need to combine them from their primals. This will be explained a bit later.
tc.research_page.RESEARCH.8=You continue doing this until you have formed a pattern connecting all the starting aspects. The outer aspects need not be connected to all the others, they simply need to form a connected whole.<BR>Once this is done the research will complete and the research note will turn into a discovery.<LINE>NOTE: Placing and removing aspects from the hex grid consumes ink from your scribing tools. If it runs out you will not be able to proceed until you refill it.
tc.research_page.RESEARCH.9=§l§nCombining Aspects§r<BR>Simply click on those aspects you wish to combine or drag them into the runic circles in area §l4§r. The selected aspects will appear in area §l4§r and when you have two selected pressing the purple button will attempt to combine them. If successful you should see what was gained in the bottom right and it should appear in area §l3§r.<BR>The component aspects are consumed even if the combination did not result in valid compound aspect.
tc.research_page.RESEARCH.10=§l§nSecondary Research§r<BR>Hexagonal icons indicate Secondary research. Much like primary research you just need to click on them. However instead of gaining a research note, you will simply learn the research directly. Secondary research does not require you to perform the research at the table, but they do cost experience levels to learn.
tc.research_page.RESEARCH.11=§l§n(2) Exploration§r<BR><BR>While many researches are available from the start, some require knowledge that cannot be learned at a table while others are hidden completely until the some mystery is uncovered.<BR>You do this by exploration and examining objects in the world.<BR>The first thing you will need to do is construct a §5Thaumometer§0. By pointing the §5Thaumometer§0 at objects or creatures and holding the right mouse button you will start examining them. 
tc.research_page.RESEARCH.12=The process does not take long, but your movement speed is reduced while it is occurring.<BR>Once complete you will be notified if you have discovered a clue.<BR>The exact nature of the clue might not be immediately apparent. Check your Thaumonomicon to see if any new research icons have been revealed (indicated by a gold star), or if new knowledge had been added to existing research (shown by a green plus).<BR>Usually new research discovered in this fashion will have amber icons.
#
tc.research_name.KNOWFRAG=知识碎片
tc.research_text.KNOWFRAG=遗落的卷章碎片
tc.research_page.KNOWFRAG.1=In your travels you might happen upon fragments of ancient and lost knowledge.<BR>When used they will grant you a small amount of experience.<BR>They might have other uses as well...
#
tc.research_name.ASPECTS=魔力要素
tc.research_text.ASPECTS=万物构造之源
tc.research_page.ASPECTS.1=一切造物(道具,对象及生物)均系于被名为§5“要素”§0的魔力元素.要素描绘了物品的构成及其对魔力元素的偏向.普通的岩石可能蕴含Terra(即拉丁文的大地)要素,而更复杂的事物,比如树木,甚或生物则可能蕴含多种数量不等的要素.目前已经有50余种要素被发现.<LINE>有两类截然不同的要素: §5元始要素§0以及§5复合要素§0.
tc.research_page.ASPECTS.2=§l元始要素§r是六种最基本的要素类型:§6Aer§0(风之要素),§2Terra§0(地之要素),§cIgnis§0(火之要素),§3Aqua§0(水之要素),§fOrdo§0(秩序要素),§8Perditio§0(混沌要素).<BR>它们是构成其它要素的基础.<BR>§l复合要素§r由两种其它要素复合而成.相对简单的复合要素由两种元始要素复合而成,但也存在一些经过多次复合,非常复杂的复合要素.<BR>举简单的例子来说,比如§2Terra§0(地之要素)与§3Aqua§0(水之要素)复合可以得到Victus(生命要素).
tc.research_page.ASPECTS.3=若想要查看一个物品所具备的要素,需要在选中物品时按下潜行键(默认shift),这样你就能看见其蕴含要素的种类和数量.但是你需要先对该物品进行初步的研究,否则其蕴含的要素会显示未知.<LINE>要素在一定程度上分离于其对象,并且作为纯粹的本质物,要素非常具有价值：无论是用作合成的工具还是用于魔法研究.<BR>魔力通常存储于法杖中,但它也可能以液相存储,此时我们通常称其为§5要素源质§0,为方便起见,本手册中有时也统一简称其为要素.
#
tc.research_name.NODES=灵气和节点
tc.research_text.NODES=魔法无所不在
tc.research_page.NODES.1=The §5Aura§0 is a field of magical energy prevalent throughout the world. Its origin is unclear. Some believe it is the accumulated life force of living beings, while others believe it to merely be another type of energy seeping in from some other place. The last theory seems to be most likely, as the aura is often found surrounding a node of concentrated mystical energy known as an §5Aura Node§0.<BR>The aura has varying levels of energy for each primal. For example, auras near water often has more §3Aqua§0, while those in a desert would have more §cIgnis§0.
tc.research_page.NODES.2=The aura varies from chunk to chunk based on this. If you the aura in an area becomes depleted then aura will flow in from neighboring areas that have higher energy values. The levels will never quite equalize as the aura acts more like an ocean of thick glue than water.<BR>The aura can also become tainted and gain the §5Vitium§0 (flux) aspect. Flux is 'thicker' and tends gather more in discrete areas before flowing to neighboring chunks. Auras that fall too far below their base levels can also generate Flux.<BR>If too much flux gathers in an area it can lead to §lTaint§r. For more information on taint see the relevant section in your Thaumonomicon.
tc.research_page.NODES.3=Aura nodes act like a doorway to some other mystical realm through which magical energy seeps. Each node is usually 'tuned' to a §5Primal Aspects§0, but rarely a node may be tuned to a §5Compound Aspect§0.<BR>Nodes cannot be tapped directly, but do slowly replenish the aura around them.<BR>Generally the rate of replenishment seems to vary with the phases of the moon with the full moon having the highest rates.<BR>The size of the node is also directly related to how quickly it will replenish the aura.
tc.research_page.NODES.4=Aura nodes are hard to see with the naked eye, but faint glimmers of light often betray their presence. Often the only way to determine their presence is to look for elevated aura levels in a localized area.<BR>Nearby nodes often attract each and will move closer together. When they get close enough they will merge with varying results, but usually resulting in a larger node containing features of one or both the original nodes.<BR>There are many different kinds of nodes to be found, but as yet you know very little about them.
tc.research_page.NODES.A=§l§nAstral Nodes§r<BR>These nodes seems to react to light - the greater the amount of light, the faster they recharge the aura.  
tc.research_page.NODES.D=§l§nDark Nodes§r<BR>These nodes operate best in darkness and when the moon is waning. Furthermore the area around such nodes is often quite sinister and dangerous as if they are tapping into some evil and dangerous mystical realm.
tc.research_page.NODES.H=§l§nHungry Nodes§r<BR>Instead of recharging the aura, these nodes slowly drain it instead. These nodes seem to increase in size and strength the more aura they consume.<BR>Many thaumaturges speculate that what you call a hungry node may merely be a node seen from the other side, but if that was true then and normal nodes would also grow in size and hungry nodes would be far more common. Fortunately, they are not.
tc.research_page.NODES.P=§l§nPure Nodes§r<BR>Pure nodes are always a welcome find. They slowly remove any flux from the surrounding aura.
tc.research_page.NODES.T=§l§nTainted Nodes§r<BR>These nodes are mystically tainted. The energy they tap into has been fouled and will occasionally create flux in the aura they are replenishing.
tc.research_page.NODES.U=§l§nUnstable Nodes§r<BR>These nodes are highly unstable and the type of aspect they replenish will occasionally change to some other random primal.
#
tc.research_name.ORE=矿石
tc.research_text.ORE=深度发掘
tc.research_page.ORE.1=§l§nVis Crystals§r<BR><IMG>thaumcraft:textures/research/research4.png:0:0:128:128:.6</IMG><BR>On occasion there is so much primal energy in an aura that it will settle into rock from which vis infused crystals will grow. As long as they are fed vis they will continue to grow and even spread.<BR>Once the aura dips low enough the 
tc.research_page.ORE.2=energy once again dissipates out of the crystals, replenishing the aura and causing the crystals to crumble. In effect, they are natural, or in this case, supernatural vis batteries. They will never crumble away completely and at least a small remnant of the crystal will remain.<BR>These crystals can be harvested for elemental shards that have many uses in Thaumaturgy.<BR><IMG>thaumcraft:textures/research/research3.png:0:104:96:16:1</IMG><BR>You know of no way to only harvest some of the crystals. It is a matter of all or none.
tc.research_page.ORE.3=§l§nCinnabar§r<BR><IMG>thaumcraft:textures/research/research3.png:128:128:128:128:.6</IMG><BR>This reddish ore is found deep underground and when smelted produces quicksilver.<BR><BR><IMG>thaumcraft:textures/items/quicksilver.png:0:0:255:255:0.0625</IMG>
tc.research_page.ORE.4=§l§nAmber§r<BR><IMG>thaumcraft:textures/research/research3.png:0:128:128:128:.6</IMG><BR>This ore is found near the surface and when mined drops chunks of amber.<BR><BR><IMG>thaumcraft:textures/items/amber.png:0:0:255:255:0.0625</IMG>
#
tc.research_name.PLANTS=植物&树木
tc.research_text.PLANTS=神奇植物
tc.research_page.PLANTS.1=§l§nGreatwood Trees§r<BR><IMG>thaumcraft:textures/research/research4.png:128:128:128:128:.6</IMG><BR>These large and majestic trees can be found dotted all over the countryside.<BR>Their wood is able to absorb impressive amounts of magic making it a popular component in the crafting of magical devices.
tc.research_page.PLANTS.2=§l§nSilverwood Trees§r<BR><IMG>thaumcraft:textures/research/research4.png:0:128:128:128:.6</IMG><BR>These rare and magical trees are a wondrous sight. Their leaves shimmer with magical energy and their pale, soft wood is valued for its purifying properties.<BR>The trees magical nature is such that aura nodes often form within their hearts - this feature alone makes a silverwood sapling a prize beyond measure.
tc.research_page.PLANTS.3=§l§nShimmerleaf§r<BR><IMG>thaumcraft:textures/research/research4.png:128:0:128:128:.6</IMG><BR>The strange, glowing flowers only grow in the shadow of Silverwood Trees. They can be harvested and pulped to produce quicksilver.<BR><BR><IMG>thaumcraft:textures/items/quicksilver.png:0:0:255:255:0.0625</IMG>
tc.research_page.PLANTS.4=§l§nCinderpearl§r<BR><IMG>thaumcraft:textures/research/research5.png:0:0:128:128:.6</IMG><BR>Found only in the hottest of climes, these plants burn with elemental fire. They can be harvested and ground to produce a fine powder akin to Blaze powder.
tc.research_page.PLANTS.5=§l§nVishroom§r<BR><IMG>thaumcraft:textures/research/research5.png:0:128:128:128:.6</IMG><BR><BR><BR>This strange, glowing mushroom can only be found growing in magical forests.<BR>They have hallucinogenic properties so one must be careful not to approach too closely. 
#
tc.research_name.CRYSTALFARMER=Crystal Farmer
tc.research_text.CRYSTALFARMER=Helping them grow
tc.research_page.CRYSTALFARMER.1=You have made a couple of discoveries that have given you the ability to turn vis shards into 'plantable' vis crystals on stone.<BR>What is more, you can now pluck a single shard from a crystal growth without having to break it - simply right click on it with your wand.
#
tc.research_name.RESEARCHER1=Research Expertise
tc.research_text.RESEARCHER1=Knowledge is Power
tc.research_page.RESEARCHER1.1=你越发擅长于研究.<BR>当你移除放入六边形的要素,会有25%的几率取回研究点.<BR>并且当鼠标悬停在其上方时你还能够看到你需要融合成何种要素.<BR>You are also able to see what aspects you need to combine to create an aspect you are hovering over.<BR>Lastly it gives you the ability to consume a knowledge fragment to add one point to each primal. 
#
tc.research_name.RESEARCHER2=研究精通
tc.research_text.RESEARCHER2=力量就是知识
tc.research_page.RESEARCHER2.1=你越发精通于研究.<BR>当你移除放入六边形的要素,会有50%的几率取回研究点.<BR>此外放置要素时也有10%的几率不消耗研究点.<BR>最后,在研究台界面中,你还能够通过按住shfit点击你想要制造出的要素,以融合要素得到它.如果你有足够用以融合的要素,它们会自动融合成你要制造的复合要素.
#
tc.research_name.BASICGOLEMANCY=Basic Golemancy
tc.research_text.BASICGOLEMANCY=Motion Controlled
tc.research_page.BASICGOLEMANCY.1=You have studied the basic, primitive golems anyone can create and found them lacking. They have potentional, but it is not possible to control them.<BR>You are sure you can do better.
#
tc.research_name.BASICTHAUMATURGY=基础法杖工艺
tc.research_text.BASICTHAUMATURGY=你的第一柄工具
tc.research_page.BASICTHAUMATURGY.1=The casting wand is your most basic, but also your most important tool. It is what you use to craft objects, activate blocks like the crucible, and countless other tasks.<BR>The most basic wand stores a very limited amount of magical energy (called vis) that it uses to perform its tasks. The replenish the energy in a wand you must simply hold it in your hand and it will draw vis from the aura.<BR>While holding a wand you will see a indicator on the top left of the screen that shows how much vis is stored within the wand.
tc.research_page.BASICTHAUMATURGY.2=按住shift时会显示标注魔力数量的额外数字以及完成特定功能时使用魔力的可能减免.<BR>法杖使用杖柄和两个杖端制作而成.随着研究的深入,你一定能发现许多不同的杖柄以及杖端材料来制作各种强力法杖.在普通合成台中只能制作最基础的法杖.而其他法杖均需要在§5奥术工作台§0中消耗魔力制作.<BR>最基础的法杖使用普通的木材和铁制作,都是些最廉价的魔法材料.
#
tc.research_name.NODETAPPER1=进阶灵气引流术
tc.research_text.NODETAPPER1=取走全部
tc.research_page.NODETAPPER1.1=Usually the process of drawing vis from the aura with a wand is quite slow... but not anymore.<BR>You have discovered a more efficient way of tapping into the aura, doubling the normal draw rate. In addition you no longer need to hold the wand in your hand to do this, merely having it on your hotbar is sufficient.
#
tc.research_name.NODETAPPER2=大师灵气引流术
tc.research_text.NODETAPPER2=你的魔力都属于我们了
tc.research_page.NODETAPPER2.1=You have added further refinements to the methods you use to tap the aura.<BR>You are now able to draw vis three times faster than normal. Furthermore you will recharge wands anywhere in your inventory, not just in your hand or hotbar.
#
tc.research_name.AURAMANIP1=Basic Aura Manipulation
tc.research_text.AURAMANIP1=Let the magic flow
tc.research_page.AURAMANIP1.1=You have made a few interesting discoveries regarding the aura and it is high time you start putting that knowledge to use. You have created a totem that pushes vis away from itself - the Totem of Dispersal.<BR>As the name suggests it takes vis near the totem and spreads it over a wider area.<BR>Messing with the aura is not without risk however and the totem has a small chance of converting the vis into flux instead of moving it.<BR>The totem requires that crystal shards be placed in its inventory to act as fuel and to determine what type of vis is effected.  
tc.research_page.AURAMANIP1.2=Each totem has an inner and outer area in which it operates. By default the inner area consists of the chunk in which it is located while the outer area consists of the 8 chunks surrounding the inner area.<BR>The dispersal totem moves vis from its inner area towards the outer area.<LINE>You also know how to craft two different totem poles. These poles must be placed below a totem and each totem can have up to 5 poles located below it. These poles modify the inner and outer areas that the totem effects. 
tc.research_page.AURAMANIP1.3=For example, a Dispersal totem with 1 inner and 2 outer poles will draw from vis from the green chunks below and push it towards the blue chunks.<IMG>thaumcraft:textures/research/research3.png:168:0:80:80:1</IMG>   
#
tc.research_name.AURAMANIP2=Totem of Attraction
tc.research_text.AURAMANIP2=Drawing it in
tc.research_page.AURAMANIP2.1=The Totem of Attraction works in much the same way is the Totem of Dispersal, except that it draws vis from the outer area and moves it towards the inner area.    
#
tc.research_name.AURAPOLESTABLE=Stabilizing Totem Pole
tc.research_text.AURAPOLESTABLE=Smoothing the flow
tc.research_page.AURAPOLESTABLE.1=This totem pole has a stabilizing effect on the totem it supports. It reduces the chance that flux is created during aura manipulation.
#
tc.research_name.THAUMOMETER=魔导透镜
tc.research_text.THAUMOMETER=魔力感应仪
tc.research_page.THAUMOMETER.1=This Thaumometer is one of the most useful and important tools in a thaumaturgists arsenal, second only to the wand.<BR>Firstly it allows you to scan objects, creatures or mystical phenomena and determine their magical make-up. You simply need to click on things to scan them.<BR>Secondly They display the current aura in the chunk you are located. Pressing 'F' while holding it allows you to change what aspect of the aura it displays. 
#
tc.research_name.GOGGLES=揭示之护目镜
tc.research_text.GOGGLES=无漏不查
tc.research_page.GOGGLES.1=基于魔导透镜的原理,你将它的功能优化制作出了另一种用于探知扫描的魔法道具:揭示之护目镜.<BR>揭示之护目镜是探索神秘世界的最佳装备之一.戴上它,你不但能用肉眼看见灵气节点,还能看到相邻节点间的互动变化.<BR>它们是神秘使探索世界的重要工具之一.
#
tc.research_name.DIOPTRA=Thaumic Dioptra
tc.research_text.DIOPTRA=Revealing the Aura
tc.research_page.DIOPTRA.1=This complex device allows a thaumaturge to see the surrounding aura in a simple and clear manner.<BR>Simply insert the proper vis shard into the top of the device to have it render the aura in a 13 chunk diameter area around it.<BR>It will also occasionally mark sources of vis as sparkles on the display. While not very precise, it can be useful in finding such sources or places of interest. 
#
tc.research_name.METALLURGY=神秘锭
tc.research_text.METALLURGY=魔导金属
tc.research_page.METALLURGY.1=人们已经证实应用神秘学的理论能够轻易地处理金属材料.你首次的相关实验就发现了神秘锭.<BR>神秘锭是向普通的金属材料灌注天然魔力得到的产物.相比铁,它更坚硬,也更具附魔亲和力.<BR>这种金属广泛用于制造更高级的魔导设备.<BR>也可以用它使用惯常的合成方法制作出相应的工具,武器和装备.
tc.research_page.METALLURGY.2=While thaumium has many useful features, sometimes mundane metals are better suited to certain tasks. Brass is a sturdy, low friction metal perfectly suited to craft intricate mechanical devices.<BR>Unfortunately it is not always possible to get hold of it due to the morphic properties of the universe you may find yourself in. Fortunately you have found an alchemical method of crafting this useful metal.
#
tc.research_name.NITOR=闪耀之光
tc.research_text.NITOR=永恒的花火
tc.research_page.NITOR.1=This flame seems to be fuelled by magic itself. The number of uses for an ever burning flame seems endless, but unfortunately it seems to produce much more light than heat. Despite that it could still prove to be a steady source of energy.<BR>Nitor can also be placed in the world to act as a magical light source. It will take on the color of any dye you combine it with in a crafting table.
#
tc.research_name.ALUMENTUM=源动之焰
tc.research_text.ALUMENTUM=神秘的能量团
tc.research_page.ALUMENTUM.1=一团伴随着跳动火焰的物质,轻微的颠簸便可能导致一次剧烈的能量释放.这种不稳定的能源可能能成为很高效的燃料.<BR>如果你不是特别喜欢爆炸的话就别把它随便丢出去.
#
tc.research_name.HUNGRYCHEST=饕餮箱子
tc.research_text.HUNGRYCHEST=无需每次都打开
tc.research_page.HUNGRYCHEST.1=只要物品落在附近,饕餮箱子便能自动拾取这些物品.
#
tc.research_name.CAP_gold=金杖端
tc.research_text.CAP_gold=高调做事
tc.research_page.CAP_gold.1=金是比铁更好的魔导介质,使用金杖端的法杖在引导魔力时不会有损失.
#
tc.research_name.CAP_brass=黄铜杖端
tc.research_text.CAP_brass=Drawing in the Vis
tc.research_page.CAP_brass.1=Like gold, wands capped with this material takes no penalty when used to channel vis. More importantly however, is the fact that these caps can draw vis from the aura easier than normal, allowing the wands they are placed on to charge faster.
#
tc.research_name.CAP_thaumium=神秘杖端
tc.research_text.CAP_thaumium=Efficiency over speed
tc.research_page.CAP_thaumium.1=Thaumium is known for its ability to store and absorb magic, so using it to craft wand caps is a logical choice. It is very efficient at focusing vis of all types.<BR>Crafting these wand caps in an arcane workbench is not sufficient - they need to be infused with additional magical energy to make them usable.
#
tc.research_name.CAP_void=虚空杖端
tc.research_text.CAP_void=来自彼界之力
tc.research_page.CAP_void.1=Crafting wand caps from void metal seems counterintuitive since it seems to be highly resistant to magic, but counterintuitive is where you live now.<BR>Your gamble paid off. The metal itself may be resistant to magic and channels vis no better than gold or brass, but it can draw vis from the aura much, much quicker than normal. The magic does seem §ostrange§r somehow, but it is probably just your imagination.
#
tc.research_name.ROD_greatwood=宏伟之木杖柄
tc.research_text.ROD_greatwood=魔力存储库
tc.research_page.ROD_greatwood.1=宏伟之木的原木雕刻而成,能存储二倍于普通木材的魔力,也就是说每种魔力都能存储500vis.
#
tc.research_name.ROD_silverwood=银树杖柄
tc.research_text.ROD_silverwood=神秘核心
tc.research_page.ROD_silverwood.1=银树被证明是极其优良的魔力存储材料,每种魔力能存储1000vis.
#
tc.research_name.SCEPTRE=工艺权杖
tc.research_text.SCEPTRE=以制造为己任
tc.research_page.SCEPTRE.1=工艺权杖是一种特制法杖,它专业制造魔力物品三十年,而别无旁顾.虽无法安装法杖核心,但其若干特性仍使得它非常值得使用.<BR>首先,这种法杖额外会提供5%的魔力减免,这比其杖端能提供的还要多.<BR>其次,在其杖柄通常所提供的容量的基础上,这种法杖还能够多存储50%的魔力.<BR>类似其他法杖,工艺权杖也可以通过杖端杖柄的绝大部分组合方式制出 - 下面几页仅仅给出部分例子.
#
tc.research_name.PRIMALRODS=Elemental Wand Cores
tc.research_text.PRIMALRODS=Elemental vis storage
tc.research_page.PRIMALRODS.1=Each of these wand cores is linked to a specific primal element which grants them additional abilities.<LINE>§l§nReed Wand Core§r<BR>A wand core made from reeds has slightly greater storage potential than greatwood cores. What makes it superior to greatwood cores however is that if the level of §6Aer§0 stored inside it drops below 10%, its will slowly replenish without the use of a node.
tc.research_page.PRIMALRODS.2=§l§nBlazing Wand Core§r<BR>Blaze rods used as wand cores has slightly greater storage potential than greatwood cores. What makes it superior to greatwood cores however is that if the level of §cIgnis§0 stored inside it drops below 10%, its fiery nature will slowly replenish it.
tc.research_page.PRIMALRODS.3=§l§nObsidian Wand Core§r<BR>A wand core chiseled from obsidian has slightly greater storage potential than greatwood cores. What makes it superior to greatwood cores however is that if the level of §2Terra§0 stored inside it drops below 10%, its will slowly replenish without the use of a node.
tc.research_page.PRIMALRODS.4=§l§nIcy Wand Core§r<BR>Wand cores crafted from ice can store slightly more vis than greatwood cores. What makes it superior to greatwood cores however is that if the level of §3Aqua§0 stored inside it drops below 10%, its icy nature will slowly replenish it.
tc.research_page.PRIMALRODS.5=§l§nQuartz Wand Core§r<BR>A wand core chiseled from nether quartz has slightly greater storage potential than greatwood cores. What makes it superior to greatwood cores however is that if the level of §7Ordo§0 stored inside it drops below 10%, its will slowly replenish without the use of a node.
tc.research_page.PRIMALRODS.6=§l§nBone Wand Core§r<BR>A bone used as a wand core has slightly greater storage potential than greatwood cores. What makes it superior to greatwood cores however is that if the level of §8Perditio§0 stored inside it drops below 10%, its will slowly replenish without the use of a node.
#
tc.research_name.PRIMALSTAVES=Elemental Staves 
tc.research_text.PRIMALSTAVES=Elemental vis storage
tc.research_page.PRIMALSTAVES.1=Like the elemental wand cores, these stave cores are linked to a specific primal element which grants them additional abilities and slowly replenish their vis stores if they get low enough. They can store 1750 vis of each type.
#
tc.research_name.ROD_greatwood_staff=魔法手杖
tc.research_text.ROD_greatwood_staff=末端带把手的巫师之杖
tc.research_page.ROD_greatwood_staff.1=法杖是神秘使的必备行头,但有时候你总会期望能用上更酷炫的款式.魔法手杖基本上只是一种更大号的法杖.它们能存储更多魔力.<BR>由于相比法杖它们造得个头更大也更坚固,应急情况也能用作武器.<BR>不幸的是,这也使得它并不适宜用作复杂工艺,且缺乏奥术工作台或类似制作平台所需的精细控制能力.
tc.research_page.ROD_greatwood_staff.2=宏伟之木制成的手杖存储魔力是同等材料的法杖的2倍,能够存储每种魔力达1250vis.
#
tc.research_name.ROD_silverwood_staff=银树杖芯
tc.research_text.ROD_silverwood_staff=魔力入髓
tc.research_page.ROD_silverwood_staff.1=这种银树制成的魔杖能够容纳每种类型的魔力2500vis.
#
tc.research_name.ROD_primal_staff=元始杖芯
tc.research_text.ROD_primal_staff=融合的元素能量
tc.research_page.ROD_primal_staff.1=这种杖芯中韵动着潜在的能量.<BR>它由所有次一级的杖芯融合制成 - 其魔力容量等同于银树杖芯且能够像各种元始要素对应的杖芯那样恢复魔力.<BR>最后,它还会使得安装的法杖核心自动附带一级的潜能附魔效果.<BR>这玩意儿在任何神秘使的装备库里都算得上真正潜能十足的工具.
#
tc.research_name.FOCUSFIRE=法杖核心
tc.research_text.FOCUSFIRE=形式遇上功能
tc.research_page.FOCUSFIRE.1=得益于一些细致的实验,即使是最基础的法杖,你也为其找到了扩展功能的方法.<BR>通过融合魔力水晶晶簇和石英水晶,并灌注以魔力,你将能够将水晶排布成神秘的阵列.<BR>若通过该阵列汇聚特定类型和数量的魔力,那么它将重塑天然魔力,使其实用,可控,且面向特定的任务.
tc.research_page.FOCUSFIRE.2=为法杖安装核心操作并不复杂 - 只需在持有法杖时按下F按键,就能安装上你携带的核心.长按F能够切换你携带的不同核心.<LINE>你初次进行的实验涉及火焰成形原理,这使得你制造出一种简单而实用的核心.<BR>它能够向前方发射锥形的火焰,在灼热的气浪中焚尽一切.
#
tc.research_name.FOCUSFROST=法杖核心:寒霜
tc.research_text.FOCUSFROST=复仇最好是一道冷菜
tc.research_page.FOCUSFROST.1=这种法杖核心能够让法杖成为投掷霜星的战斗兵器.<BR>使用这柄法杖瞄准时需要相当小心,因为四溅的霜星有时可能会打坏一些脆弱的物品.注意不要在脆弱的建筑附近使用它,此外,霜星能够化水为冰.
#
tc.research_name.FOCUSSHOCK=法杖核心:震击
tc.research_text.FOCUSSHOCK=雷霆与风暴
tc.research_page.FOCUSSHOCK.1=这种法杖核心能够汇聚元素能量形成雷电球来伤害敌人.
#
tc.research_name.FOCUSEXCAVATION=法杖核心:采掘
tc.research_text.FOCUSEXCAVATION=大地惊骇
tc.research_page.FOCUSEXCAVATION.1=这种法杖核心能够将法杖变成可以轻松移动泥土沙石的工具.<BR>将这种工具指向你想挖掘的地方,让魔法完成剩下的所有事情.更坚硬的材料将会花费更长的时间,除了泥土,石头和常见材料外的东西也会更花时间.
#
tc.research_name.FOCUSTRADE=法杖核心:更替
tc.research_text.FOCUSTRADE=这个换成那个
tc.research_page.FOCUSTRADE.1=这种法杖核心能够将法杖变成能够用魔法来使得转换你放置的方块与你口袋中的方块的工具.<BR>按住潜行(shift)右击选中某种方块.当你的口袋中有这种方块的时候,点击你面前的方块,你之前选中的方块就会与之发生替换.若右击则会对一片方块发生作用.<BR>你必须携带足够多的替换用方块,被替换的方块会被放置到你的物品栏中.只有至少有一面暴露在外的方块或者非实体能够被替换.
#
tc.research_name.FOCUSHELLBAT=法杖核心:九狱
tc.research_text.FOCUSHELLBAT=小怪物们
tc.research_page.FOCUSHELLBAT.1=你的下界之旅让你充分领略到了九狱焱蝠的可怕.你已经发现如何召唤出这种恐怖的小怪物并指挥它们飞向敌人.好评.
#
tc.research_name.FOCUSPORTABLEHOLE=法杖核心:便携式洞穴
tc.research_text.FOCUSPORTABLEHOLE=妈妈再也不担心你回不了家
tc.research_page.FOCUSPORTABLEHOLE.1=你已经能够成功地使用魔力创造异次元空间.使用该核心的法杖能够在墙壁或者其他表面打通异次元通道通往彼端.<BR>通道只能维持数秒,且根据通道深度会从法杖中抽取不等数量的魔力以完成施法.<BR>异次元通道在一些特定方块或者比较复杂的物体表面都不能创建.
#
tc.research_name.FOCUSPRIMAL=法杖核心:元始
tc.research_text.FOCUSPRIMAL=天然魔力
tc.research_page.FOCUSPRIMAL.1=What madness possessed you to create this thing? This focus seems wildly dangerous and only a lunatic will attempt to use it anywhere but the most controlled environments.<BR>Granted, the orb of raw primal energy it creates is quite devastating, but its path of travel is erratic at best and downright malicious at worst.<BR>It  does beg further study however: The orb shows some interesting dimensional properties and it exhibits energy patterns you have only seen in wisps and aura nodes.
#
tc.research_name.FOCUSPOUCH=法杖核心手袋
tc.research_text.FOCUSPOUCH=法杖核心的便携口袋
tc.research_page.FOCUSPOUCH.1=当你已经收集了一定数量的核心后如何方便得携带它们就成了恼人的问题,核心手袋就能有效解决该问题.<BR>当你试图切换法杖核心时,会首先检查手袋里的核心类型,且卸除的核心也会优先放置在手袋内.你也可以右键打开手袋来放置或者取出核心.
#
tc.research_name.BOOTSTRAVELLER=旅行者之靴
tc.research_text.BOOTSTRAVELLER=专业行走设备
tc.research_page.BOOTSTRAVELLER.1=这双富含神秘的魔力工艺技巧的靴子能让任何旅行者的旅途变得更轻松愉快.<BR>它能够让你移动得比平常更加迅速,并且能够直接掠过较高的台子.它也能够让你跳得更高,落得更远.<BR>另外,它还能让你像鱼一样破浪而行,虽然是一条相对缓慢和笨拙的鱼,可也算条鱼嘛!
#
tc.research_name.PHIAL=玻璃安瓿
tc.research_text.PHIAL=神秘容器
tc.research_page.PHIAL.1=玻璃安瓿能够盛放各种形式的液体或者其他物质,但最为重要的是它可以容纳要素源质.<BR>液相的要素源质难以收集,且会彻底污染盛放它的玻璃安瓿,因此玻璃安瓿只能作为一种一次性使用的消耗品.
#
tc.research_name.TABLE=台桌
tc.research_text.TABLE=一些设备安装所需
tc.research_page.TABLE.1=台桌并非仅仅是个装饰性的方块 - 比如在魔法实验中,它还能作为创建奥术工作台和研究台的基础部件.
#
tc.research_name.ARCTABLE=奥术工作台
tc.research_text.ARCTABLE=魔力合成
tc.research_page.ARCTABLE.1=对着放置好的台桌使用法杖(右键)就能创建一个奥术工作台奥术工作台囊括了普通的木制工作台的功能.<BR>除去普通的合成,这个工作台还能用于制作一些神秘学上独有的道具.合成这种物品时你需要将你的法杖放置在工作台右上角的位置,这样制作过程中需要的要素就可以由这个法杖来供给.<BR>合成所需何种魔力会显示在合成网格周围的六角徽记中.
#
tc.research_name.RESTABLE=研究台
tc.research_text.RESTABLE=汇焦知识
tc.research_page.RESTABLE.1=The Research table is created by clicking on a wooden table with a set of Scribing tools.<BR>The research table is the most important tool for any thaumaturge. It is used to unlock all the hidden secrets of the universe and discover new ways of harnessing magic. 
#
tc.research_name.THAUMONOMICON=魔导手册
tc.research_text.THAUMONOMICON=知识的宝库
tc.research_page.THAUMONOMICON.1=只需简单地对着放置下的书架轻轻挥舞你的法杖,就能制作出属于你的魔导手册.<BR>魔导手册将是神秘学方面全面权威的参考手册.它会列出你当前全部的研究发现,并且在大体上(但并不确保你完全了解仍然有多少未知可供探索寻觅)让你对仍然有多少可以研究的内容有一个总的印象.<BR>每当你阅读了记录新研究成果的卷轴,它会自动把相关内容添加记录到手册中.建议在右键使用卷轴时适当留意下其研究需要的要素(正常情况下使用过的卷轴会消失),这些知识可能对你的朋友有所帮助.这样你就可以自由浏览这些研究发现相关的合成以及一些细致的信息.
#
tc.research_name.CRUCIBLE=坩埚
tc.research_text.CRUCIBLE=沸腾并且冒着泡
tc.research_page.CRUCIBLE.1=只需对着放置在地上的普通炼药锅使用你的法杖,你就能得到这种具有魔力的坩埚.<BR>坩埚对神秘使来说是重要的工具.它能够让你将常态的物品分解成其蕴含的要素并且如你所愿地组合.<BR>坩埚需要放置在一个长久热源的上方(用打火石点燃下界岩来构建)并且装满水.当水开始沸腾并冒着气泡的时候可以向其中投掷物品,这样物品就会分解破坏成基本要素.<BR>如果坩埚中要素组合符合特定搭配,
tc.research_page.CRUCIBLE.2=你可以向坩埚内丢入催化剂这种特殊物品.催化剂将作为核心聚合要素,且转换成全新的物品后,会从坩埚中弹出.<BR>多余的源质会留存在坩埚中以备后用,但长期让要素残留在坩埚中无疑不是好主意.<BR>使用坩埚制作物品还会消耗坩埚中少量的水,因此你最终会需要重新添水.<BR>坩埚中的要素会持续降解.复合要素会降解成组成它的要素之一,而元始要素会蒸发消失.
tc.research_page.CRUCIBLE.3=这不仅仅会造成资源的浪费,蒸发和降解的源质还会造成诸多奇怪的副作用.<BR>你可以对着坩埚使用法杖清空坩埚中的要素制作物品,但这会让坩埚中的要素全部流失到大气中…因此你并不希望经常这样做.
tc.research_page.CRUCIBLE.4=下面是一些所有人皆可使用的炼金配方.<LINE>§n平衡碎片<BR><BR>向普通的魔力碎片灌注其余五种它不具有的元始要素的魔力碎片,最终得到的就是这种六大元始要素相互平衡的,能够与元始能量完美共鸣的水晶碎片.<BR> 在熔炉中冶炼平衡碎片能够得到世界盐(参见后文).
tc.research_page.CRUCIBLE.5=§n世界盐§r<BR><BR>世界盐,或其广为人知的名称神秘使之盐,是加热衡之碎片使其分解得到的细粉.<BR>正如凡俗世界的盐一样,神秘使之盐也能够给所有那些普通的魔法配方或仪轨增添美妙的滋味(这是个隐喻).它是一种强力的粘合剂,能够让彼此间最暌离的魔力要素聚合在一起.
#
tc.research_name.ENCHFABRIC=魔力布匹
tc.research_text.ENCHFABRIC=丝般柔滑
tc.research_page.ENCHFABRIC.1=By combining spider silk and wool and infusing it with primal vis, you can creat a silky length of magical cloth that has numerous uses.<BR>You also have patterns to create cloth robes from the magical fabric. These robes have similar protective properties to leather armor, but they are much more durable than mundane materials could ever be.<BR>They also hold mystical enchantments very well and can hold powerful magic much better than even expensive armor.  
tc.research_page.ENCHFABRIC.2=当穿戴法袍施法时你能够更高效地使用数种法术.<BR>类似皮革套装,你可以对法袍进行染色.
#
tc.research_name.ENCHANT=附魔
tc.research_text.ENCHANT=新附魔技术
tc.research_page.ENCHANT.1=神秘使懂得许多独特的附魔技术.§n急迫§r<BR>进行该附魔的鞋子能够让穿戴者在地上行走时健步如飞,附魔等级越高,增幅速度越多.<BR>§n修复§r<BR>该附魔能够从灵气中吸取魔力来缓慢地修复物品耐久.
tc.research_page.ENCHANT.2=附魔等级越高,修复速度越快.这种附魔只能对部分神秘物品生效.
#
tc.research_name.ELEMENTALTOOLS=Elemental Tools
tc.research_text.ELEMENTALTOOLS=Harnessing the elements
tc.research_page.ELEMENTALTOOLS.1=With the discovery of infusion, you have found a way to bind the primal elements into tools and weapons, each with unique and powerful properties.<LINE>§l§nAxe of the Stream§r<BR>By combining water shards and a thaumium axe, you have created a tool that embodies the aspects of motion and flow.<BR>It functions like a normal axe on all materials except natural logs and trees. When used on them the axe seeks to furthest block of the same type that is still connected to the
tc.research_page.ELEMENTALTOOLS.2=block you are attempting to harvest and harvests that one instead.<BR>In effect you will chop trees from the top down even if you hit the bottom-most block.<BR>Any wood chopped in this fashion will automatically float towards you.<BR>If you press and hold right click the axe will axe will draw all nearby items towards you - not just wood it chopped.<BR>If shift is held while using this tool all its special properties are suspended and it functions like a normal axe.
tc.research_page.ELEMENTALTOOLS.3=§l§nPickaxe of the Core§r<BR>By infusing a thaumium pickaxe with fire shards, you have created a pickaxe that glows with the heat of a forge.<BR>When you mine ore blocks there is a chance that you will mine a cluster instead. Native clusters are much easier to process and produces double the normal amount of metal when smelted.<BR>It can also be used to sound out any surface you right click against to find out what valuable ores, lava or water can be found nearby.
tc.research_page.ELEMENTALTOOLS.4=If shift is held while using this tool all its special properties are suspended and it functions like a normal pickaxe.
tc.research_page.ELEMENTALTOOLS.5=§l§nSword of the Zephyr§r<BR>You have merged the elemental fury of air shards with a thaumium sword.<BR>When used to strike a foe, the blade will sweep in a wide arc, hitting additional foes near your main target.<BR>While blocking the sword will conjure a sphere of whirling winds around you, pushing enemies and loose objects away and deflecting incoming projectiles.<BR>While blocking it will also slowly lift you into the air.
tc.research_page.ELEMENTALTOOLS.6=§l§nShovel of the Earthmover§r<BR>Combining earth shards with a thaumium shovel you have created a peerless digging implement.<BR>When used to dig earth, sand and similar materials it will dig a 3x3 area.<BR>If you right click on the side of a block, it will attempt to place a 3x3 section of the same material in the world as long as you have sufficient blocks in your inventory.<BR>The orientation of both the digging and construction depends on the face you dug or clicked.<BR>If shift is pressed you can see where blocks will be placed
tc.research_page.ELEMENTALTOOLS.7=in the world and you can change the orientation of how blocks are placed by pressing 'G' on the keyboard. Blocks can be placed either parallel to the block face selected, or extending out of the face vertically or horizontally. <BR>If shift is held while using this tool all its special properties are suspended and it functions like a normal shovel.
tc.research_page.ELEMENTALTOOLS.8=§l§nHoe of Growth§r<BR>By merging the magical energy from order and entropy shards with a thaumium hoe, you have created a farming implement with few equals.<BR>When used to till fields, it will till a 3x3 area instead of just a single block.<BR>When used to crops or other plants it will act as bonemeal to promote its growth, though at a higher cost to its durability. It might even be able to grow plants that normal bonemeal can't.<BR>If shift is held while using this tool all its special properties are suspended and it functions like a normal hoe.
#
tc.research_name.ALCHEMICALDUPLICATION=炼金复制
tc.research_text.ALCHEMICALDUPLICATION=好东西不可能拥有太多
tc.research_page.ALCHEMICALDUPLICATION.1=这世上有许多物质本就是炼金材料.<BR>小心翼翼地向它们添加合适的要素,就能够让它们变得更多.
#
tc.research_name.ALCHEMICALMANUFACTURE=炼金制造
tc.research_text.ALCHEMICALMANUFACTURE=条条路儿通罗马
tc.research_page.ALCHEMICALMANUFACTURE.1=You have mastered the basics of alchemy and are now ready to try creating more complex substances from scratch.<BR>You have formulated several recipes that create normally hard to get substances and items via alchemy.
#
tc.research_name.ENTROPICPROCESSING=混沌过程
tc.research_text.ENTROPICPROCESSING=让事情变得更糟?
tc.research_page.ENTROPICPROCESSING.1=魔法物品或者凡俗物品做起来都令人满意,但有时候你只是想将物品分解成基本的组成部分.还有比向它们添加混沌能量更简单的事情吗?<BR>其实这主意足可罗列若干理由陈述其糟糕,但哪有不冒点风险就能取得进展的道理呢?
#
tc.research_name.PUREMETAL=金属晶簇化
tc.research_text.PUREMETAL=将金属结晶成原矿簇
tc.research_page.PUREMETAL.1=Native clusters are rare concentrations of metals in its purest form. You have discovered a way to purify and concentrate normal ore into a native cluster.<BR>When smelted these clusters produces twice the normal amount of ingots.
#
tc.research_name.TRANSMETAL=嬗变术:炼铁术
tc.research_text.TRANSMETAL=Transformation of metals into other metals
tc.research_page.TRANSMETAL.1=You have discovered a way to multiply metals by steeping nuggets of that metal in §5metallum§0 and other aspects.
#
tc.research_name.TALLOW=魔力油脂
tc.research_text.TALLOW=魔力熬制的油脂
tc.research_page.TALLOW.1=在坩埚中熬炼肉块,你制作出一种具有多种奥术用途的魔力油脂.<BR>这种油脂可以用作制作蜡烛.在奥术工作台中可以使用颜料为蜡烛染色.
#
tc.research_name.DISTILESSENTIA=要素蒸馏
tc.research_text.DISTILESSENTIA=收获要素
tc.research_page.GOLEMBELL.1=Golems are notoriously bad at following verbal commands, but this bell allows you to avoid all that.<BR>Simply right click on a golem to select it. Once that is done a glowing, gear like circle will appear indicating the golems 'home' location and the side it is attached to.<BR> You are now able to right click anywhere in the world to link the golem to blocks, locations or inventories it may interact with. Clicking on the same location will either unmark it, or cycle through different colors if the golem is able to interact with different colored markers.
tc.research_page.GOLEMBELL.2=Shift + right-clicking on a marked location will always clear it and pressing F will clear all marked locations.<LINE>Left-clicking on a golem picks it up with all its current upgrades and settings intact. Shift + left-clicking picks up the golem, but removes its core and any attached upgrades which drops separately. There is a good chance that upgrades will be lost if you do this however. 
#
tc.research_name.DISTILESSENTIA=Essentia Distillation
tc.research_text.DISTILESSENTIA2=收获要素
tc.research_page.DISTILESSENTIA.1=In the future you will definitely need to have ready access to multiple different kinds of aspects - not just primal aspects drawn from your wand.<BR>Using basic alchemical principles you have devised a way to break down objects and convert them into essentia.<BR>The first step in this process requires an §lEssentia Smeltery§r. The smelter works much like a normal furnace by burning coal to produce heat, but instead of smelting ore into metal, it breaks down objects into a slurry of raw, unprocessed essentia. This process isn't very efficient and a small 
tc.research_page.DISTILESSENTIA.2=amount of essentia is converted into flux roughly 20% of the time.<BR>The next step in the process is to take the essentia slurry and distill it using an §lArcane Alembic§r.<BR>To work, arcane alembics need to be placed on top of a smelter. Multiple alembics can be placed on top of each other to increase storage, but it does not influence processing speed. The essentia slurry will slowly be drawn into the alembic and the individual aspected essentia separated out.<BR>If the smelter is being powered by alumentum, this distillation process is much faster.
tc.research_page.DISTILESSENTIA.3=The essentia can then be extracted out of an alembic using phials, jars or more complex means.
tc.research_page.DISTILESSENTIA.4=§nArcane Bellows§r<BR>Arcane bellows placed on the side of a smelter will greatly increase the heat it generates, allowing items to be broken down into a slurry much quicker.
#
tc.research_name.DISTILESSENTIA2=Thaumium Essentia Smeltery
tc.research_text.DISTILESSENTIA3=收获要素
tc.research_page.DISTILESSENTIA2.1=The Thaumium Smeltery works much like the basic smeltery, but it has roughly 85% efficiency instead of 80%.<BR>Its main benefit is that it breaks down essentia slurry at double the normal speed. 
#
tc.research_name.DISTILESSENTIA3=Void Metal Essentia Smeltery
tc.research_text.DISTILESSENTIA3=Harvesting essentia
tc.research_page.DISTILESSENTIA3.1=The Void Metal Smeltery works much like the basic smeltery, but it has roughly 95% efficiency instead of 80%.<BR>It breaks down essentia slurry slightly quicker than the basic smeltery, but not nearly as fast as the thaumium smeltery.
#
tc.research_name.IMPROVED_DISTILLATION=Improved Essentia Distillation
tc.research_text.IMPROVED_DISTILLATION=Essentia Harvesting... Improved
tc.research_page.IMPROVED_DISTILLATION.1=While smelters can be very fast, they could always be faster - especially the speed at which they break down the essentia slurry into usable essentia.<BR>Each Auxiliary Slurry Pump placed on the side of a smelter acts as a secondary processor, outputting refined essentia to any alembics placed above it.
#
tc.research_name.JARLABEL=要素罐子和标签
tc.research_text.JARLABEL=存储和整理要素源质
tc.research_page.JARLABEL.1=可以用§l要素罐子§r储存要素源质.<BR>将要素罐子放置在地上,它能够非常明了直观地储存源质.由于魔法的力量,使用或者存放罐子中的源质都是小菜一碟的事情.<BR>手持罐子直接点击奥术蒸馏器就可以将源质装进罐中.你也可以使用要素安瓿来填充或清空罐子.<BR>此外它们还非常便于大量而密集地进行源质储存.
tc.research_page.JARLABEL.2=空手状态下按住潜行键Shift点击罐子或者蒸馏器能够清空它们.<BR>只要罐子里装有源质,你就可以贴上§l罐子标签l§.<BR>标签将罐子锁定为接收特定类型的要素源质而不再能接收任意其他类型的源质.<BR>空手对着罐子帖着标签的一面按住潜行点击,能够取下标签.注意如果误点了其他面会清空罐子里装的源质.
tc.research_page.JARLABEL.3=你可以对着空罐子使用与某种要素绑定过的标签(在合成台中合成装有要素的安瓿与标签),这样空罐子会自动绑定到这种要素,变成对应的标签罐子.而标签上的要素仅仅只是标记,并不真的消耗源质.<BR>对着装满了要素的罐子使用,则会把罐子变成和其容纳要素相对应的标签罐子.<LINE>绑定过某种要素的标签只需要放入合成网格参与一次合成就能变回空白标签.
#
tc.research_name.INFERNALFURNACE=炼狱熔炉
tc.research_text.INFERNALFURNACE=够热?
tc.research_page.INFERNALFURNACE.1=By harnessing raw §cIgnis§0 within a furnace crafted from obsidian and netherbrick you have created a highly efficient and fuel free furnace. So efficient in fact, that occasionally it will produce bonus materials in the form of nuggets or other items.<BR>While this is essentially free, it is also very slow unless the furnace gets a steady supply of §cIgnis§0 vis from the aura. 
tc.research_page.INFERNALFURNACE.2=It should also be noted that the occasional bit of Flux escapes into the environment.<BR>Items you wish to smelt needs to be dropped into the top of the furnace and will be spit out the front.
#
ttc.research_name.BELLOWS=奥术风箱
tc.research_text.BELLOWS=煽风点火
tc.research_page.BELLOWS.1=奥术风箱功能正如其名,不过它能够自己动作,对着需要的方向发出阵阵气流.<BR>将其安装在地狱熔炉侧面和后面的开孔处(一个熔炉可以安装3个)会出现有趣的现象：蕴含魔力的气流不仅仅加快了熔炉燃烧的速度,也让火焰更加纯净,减少了咒波的产生率,增大了获得金属粒或者其他材料的额外产物的机会.
tc.research_page.BELLOWS.2=They can also be attached to normal or essentia smelteries to increase their speed.<BR>It is also possible to attach them to crucibles to reduce the time it takes for their water to boil.<BR>Bellows can be deactivated by applying a redstone signal.<BR>You are confident more uses will reveal themselves eventually. 
#
tc.research_name.ARCANESTONE=奥术石材
tc.research_text.ARCANESTONE=魔力强化的建筑材料
tc.research_page.ARCANESTONE.1=奥术石材是多种复杂的神秘构造的建筑材料.它是一种被火之元素灼烤,被地之元素强化的石材.
#
tc.research_name.INFUSION=注魔
tc.research_text.INFUSION=魔力聚变
tc.research_page.INFUSION.1=奥术合成和炼金术能达到的层度也就到此为止了.为了获得更好的东西你需要创造出更强大的魔导设备.<BR>注魔合成能够向单件物品中灌注魔力和来自其他物品的特性.比方说,你能够将风之要素以及羽毛灌注入普通石头来得到一种非常轻盈的石材.<BR>神秘学中通常很难有既轻松又简单的内容.搭建注魔台前你需要做如下准备:符文矩阵,奥术基座,以及足够数量的要素源质.
tc.research_page.INFUSION.2=当你将符文矩阵正确地放置在一个名为注魔祭坛的神秘构造上后,便能够开始进行注魔合成.<BR>符文矩阵下方,坐落于正中的基座是你用于放置被注魔物品的地方.你还需要环绕祭坛放置一些基座来放置被灌注的材料.最后你还需要在附近放置一些盛放了要素源质的罐子或者其他类似的魔力存储容器.<BR>当一切就绪,你需要使用法杖点击符文矩阵来开始注魔过程.<BR>在这个过程的第一阶段,注魔祭坛将会从附近吸取所需的要素源质.
tc.research_page.INFUSION.3=若没有足够的源质供应,注魔过程会中断 - 后文将会对这种你不希望发生的情况做进一步的阐释.<BR>当所有需求的源质被灌入目标物品后,才能开始吸收被灌注的其他物品的要素源质.仅当这些都完成后注魔才能顺利完成.<LINE>注魔合成并非毫无风险.其完整的过程实质上是把庞杂的魔法能量强制集中到单独的物品中,在这种情况下往往会发生一些不可预知的事情:<BR>
tc.research_page.INFUSION.4=比较常见的意外包括注魔过载被基座中断掉,产生咒波等,但也可能遭遇一些闻所未闻的灾难事件.<BR>由于魔力缺乏,物品掉落等未解决的问题导致而的注魔时间延迟越久,就越发有可能发生糟糕的事情.<BR>可以有多种途径来减少这些意外的影响.首先你应该尽可能对称地布置注魔祭坛 - 一定要确保你放置的基座对侧有以祭坛为原点对称的基座与之平衡.当放置被灌注材料时,也需要尽可能保证放置位置对称与平衡.
tc.research_page.INFUSION.5=altar in symmetrical formations (things like candles, skulls, crystals, etc.). These will have the effect of reducing instability.<IMG>thaumcraft:textures/research/research5.png:128:0:128:136:1</IMG>
tc.research_page.INFUSION.ANCIENT=§nAncient Stone§r<BR>The strange, ancient stone you have found has some interesting mystical properties. You believe that when used to craft the pillars for an infusion altar that it will help reduce the amount of essentia required during infusion crafting and speed up the crafting process by a small amount. It will however increase instability slightly.<BR>Should you find pedestals crafted from the same material each one will also help reduce essentia costs. Unfortunately you have been unable to craft such pedestals yourself.
tc.research_page.INFUSION.ELDRITCH=§nEldritch Stone§r<BR>The dark, eldritch stone you have discovered has some strange properties. When used to craft the infusion altar pillars it will help reduce instability and speed up the crafting process by a moderate amount. It will unfortunately increase crafting cost slightly.<BR>Should you happen accross any pedestals made from the same material it will have much the same effect. Caution should be taken to carefully balance them however as unbalanced eldritch pedestals will massively increase your instability. Unfortunately you have been unable to craft such pedestals yourself.
#
tc.research_name.INFUSIONBOOST=Infusion Boosting
tc.research_text.INFUSIONBOOST=Upgraded mystical fusion
tc.research_page.INFUSIONBOOST.1=You have found a way to improve infusion altars through the use of special blocks placed under one or more of the four altar pillars.<BR>The §5Infusion Speed Stone§0 will increase the speed at which the altar operates, but at a slight increase to costs.<BR>The §5Infusion Cost Stone§0 will decrease infusion costs, but at a slight reduction to operating speed.<BR>These stones must be placed directly under an altar pillar, but they need not be balanced for instability purposes.
#
tc.research_name.JARBRAIN=缸中之脑
tc.research_text.JARBRAIN=密封的纠缠
tc.research_page.JARBRAIN.1= -  向罐子丢一个僵尸之脑.<BR> -  添加蜘蛛眼和水.<BR> -  回想那些邪恶的念头,然后对着它挥舞你的法杖.<BR>若你能遵循上述步骤就能得到一个会动的邪恶的缸中之脑.<BR>它保留了作为僵尸的饥饿欲望却无力享用那些“美味”的脑子.但它仍然会试图收集那些在其附近死亡的生灵的思想和经验(以经验球的实体形式出现).当你摇一摇容纳它的罐子,它会放弃部分不义之财将其交予你.<BR>罐子盛满后它的上方将显示粒子效果.
#
tc.research_name.HOVERHARNESS=奥法缰绳
tc.research_text.HOVERHARNESS=它是一只鸟?
tc.research_page.HOVERHARNESS.1=You have finally managed to unlock the secret of flight. You have created a harness that anchors itself to the Thaumic Field using thaumostatic energy allowing you to defy gravity. You think quantum's and quarks might also be involved somehow.<BR>The harness is powered by vis it draws directly from the local aura. Single unit of Aer and Ignis vis provides enough power for 1 second of flight. The harness has an internal buffer that stores enough vis for 10 seconds of flight if the local aura is depleted.<BR>Pressing 'H' while wearing the harness activates or deactivates it.
tc.research_page.HOVERHARNESS.2=It can be enchanted with the Haste enchant to increase the speed at which you move while flying.<BR>The harness will not reduce your block breaking speed while you are flying with it.
#
tc.research_name.HOVERGIRDLE=奥法腰带
tc.research_text.HOVERGIRDLE=它是只灰机?
tc.research_page.HOVERGIRDLE.1=这种腰带的设计旨在配合奥法缰绳来使用.就自身而言,其浮空力非常小 - 仅够让穿戴者免受大部分的掉落伤害.<BR>但配合奥法缰绳一起使用时,它能够显著提升飞行速度.唯一的坏处是会让奥法缰绳消耗的燃料比平时稍多.
#
tc.research_name.ADVANCEDGOLEM=高级傀儡
tc.research_text.ADVANCEDGOLEM=也许我应该考虑考虑尽管...
tc.research_page.ADVANCEDGOLEM.1=你已经发现了一些在微小而重要的方面改进傀儡的方法.<BR>首先,改进后傀儡能够额外安装一个升级,尽管它们不能重复安装两次同类型的升级.<BR>其次,改进后他们移动速度会稍微快些.<BR>再次,这也能够稍微加大它们的视野范围.<BR>当然,你非常确定它们眼中偶尔流露出的狡诈与恶意不过是你的妄想而已.
#
tc.research_name.ARCANEBORE=奥术钻探机
tc.research_text.ARCANEBORE=采矿业的进化
tc.research_page.ARCANEBORE.1=你已经发现一种拥有采掘核心能力,且具有更大的工作范围的奥术设备,不仅如此,这台机器还可以无人监控地自动运行.只需要将它安装在特别的基座上,将其方向调校正确后,再提供一个法杖供能,并用红石信号激活即可.<BR>奥术钻探机需要两件东西才能正常工作.首先你需要将采掘核心放在物品栏左侧格子中,法杖核心的附魔效果也会被加成到钻探机上.
tc.research_page.ARCANEBORE.2=其次,你需要在右边格子里放置一个任意类型的镐子.镐的材料对钻探机运行效果影响很小,但其耐久直接决定钻探机的运行时间.此外,类似核心,镐子上的附魔效果也能够被加成到钻探机上.<BR>奥法钻头只能安附在奥法钻探基座的上方或下方.挖掘到的物品都会从钻探基座的喷嘴所朝方向弹出来.<BR>如果有箱子则会自动进入其物品栏.你可以用法杖改变奥术钻探机的朝向.
tc.research_page.ARCANEBORE.3=倘若向钻探机供应§8Perditio§0源质或魔力其钻探效率将大大提升.既可以使用管道供应魔力或源质,也可以使用节点中继器供应厘魔(CV).一点§8Perditio§0源质能够让钻探机以更快的速度挖掘接下来的20个方块.而作为另外一种选择的中继器系统的效率则是,每加速挖掘一个方块消耗5点CV,而钻探机每tick最多能够输入100CV.
#
tc.research_name.LEVITATOR=奥术悬浮台
tc.research_text.LEVITATOR=下面该研究怎么飞了!
tc.research_page.LEVITATOR.1=While not true flight, the Arcane Levitator is the next best thing.<BR>When placed the levitator lifts any item or creature above it up to 8 blocks into the air. A sneaking creature or player will be slowly lowered.<BR>While levitating something it consumes 2 aer CV per second from the aura.<BR>The levitator can be placed in any orientation, and when placed horizontally will push creatures along while keeping them aloft.
tc.research_page.LEVITATOR.2=A toggle on the back of the device allows you to alter the range at which it operates, but also changes the amount of CV it uses.  
#
tc.research_name.ARCANEEAR=奥术之耳
tc.research_text.ARCANEEAR=嘘,你有没有听见什么??
tc.research_page.ARCANEEAR.1=The Arcane Ear is a device that is capable of detecting the sound emitted from nearby note blocks. If it hears a note it recognizes it will emit a short redstone pulse.<BR>The Arcane Ear needs to be tuned in a manner identical to note blocks, the tone and note it listens for depends on the material it is placed against. Arcane ears can be placed against any surface.
#
tc.research_name.MIRROR=魔镜
tc.research_text.MIRROR=镜中奇缘
tc.research_page.MIRROR.1=你尝试附魔镜子,将它变成通往世界间隙那广漠虚空的传送门.投入其(或是使用管道向镜子输入)的物品将会跨越空间甚至跨越位面,然后从另外一面镜子喷出.<BR>不幸的是空间通道对像你这样的实体生物非常排斥,因此用这种魔镜来传输生物暂时是不可能的.<BR>要链接一对魔镜,你需要将其中一面镜子安装在目标位置.
tc.research_page.MIRROR.2=并用第二面镜子右击第一名镜子,并安装在需要的位置.当两面都装好后会建立连接,镜面会出现黑洞的图案.当你将物品投入其中,物品会自动从另一个镜子被抛出.<BR>魔镜只能成对链接.当安装好后不能与第三个魔镜建立链接.当你拆卸后重新安装魔镜的时候,它能够自动回忆上次建立配对的魔镜.然而,拆卸配对的魔镜后,你也能很方便地用它建立新的链接.
tc.research_page.MIRROR.3=Transporting items through mirrors places stress on the magical aura. Every now and again this causes Flux to be generated. The more items you transport, the more flux is generated..
#
tc.research_name.MIRRORHAND=魔力手镜
tc.research_text.MIRRORHAND=反思时间
tc.research_page.MIRRORHAND.1=魔力手镜类似普通的魔镜.但首先,正如其名,它可以随身携带,手持已经链接到目标魔镜的手镜右击就可以打开界面,将物品放入魔镜中的格子即可以实现传递,他们会被另一端的魔镜吐出来.<BR>其次,魔力手镜能够通过右键与新的魔镜绑定.你能够使用手镜来方便地将物品进行传输.<BR>手镜能够链接到已经链接过其他手镜的魔镜上.<BR>注意手镜只能传出物品,不能接收物品.
#
tc.research_name.PAVETRAVEL=旅行者铺路石
tc.research_text.PAVETRAVEL=缩地成寸
tc.research_page.PAVETRAVEL.1=你学会了如何向石英方块灌注大地要素的魔力.<BR>走在这种铺路砖上的人们感觉身轻如燕,脚步敏捷,弹跳力也得到加强.
#
tc.research_name.PAVEBARRIER=守卫者铺路石
tc.research_text.PAVEBARRIER=御守于外
tc.research_page.PAVEBARRIER.1=你发现一种方法能够将奥术石材转换成一种能够有效阻绝大多数生物入侵的守卫铺路石.<BR>注意这种警卫作用并不能提供百分百的防护,例如,它们并不阻止玩家进去它们圈定的区域,但它们确实能防护住大部分常见威胁.它们还会阻止傀儡穿过.<BR>使用它们时最好围成一个不间断的完整的圈,将你想守护的区域与外面的世界相对隔绝.<BR>激活的红石信号会使得该方块的特殊效果暂时失效.
tc.research_page.PAVEBARRIER.2=The color of the runes above the stone indicates its current status.<BR>Purple runes show that it is currently preventing something from passing through.<BR>Blue runes indicates it has been deactivated with a redstone signal.<BR>Red runes shows that something is preventing it from fully warding an area and a gap exists where something might be able to pass through.
#
tc.research_name.WANDPED=充能基座
tc.research_text.WANDPED=自动补魔
tc.research_page.WANDPED.1=Traveling around the countryside to recharge your wand is all good and well, but an automatic way of doing it would be much better.<BR>This specially crafted pedestal does just that - any wand placed in it will automatically draw vis from the aura to recharge itself.<BR>Wands are not the only items that can be recharged in this device - many vis holding gadgets should be rechargeble in this.
#
tc.research_name.ETHEREALBLOOM=天域花
tc.research_text.ETHEREALBLOOM=纯洁的花朵
tc.research_page.ETHEREALBLOOM.1=水银花常常生长在银树附近的阴影之中,但是它亦有自己独特的魔法属性.<BR>类似银树,水银花也潜藏着休眠中的净化魔力.你已经找到一种方法唤醒这种魔力,并将其转化为天域花.<BR>天域花,能够十分缓慢但确定无疑地恢复这片被神秘力量(包括我们通常称之为腐化的咒波污染)所污染和破坏的大地,使其重回昔日的荣光之下.虽然它并不能够直接对抗腐化,但腐化的植物会很难蔓延到天域花所处的环境中,并会渐渐趋向于枯萎死亡.
tc.research_page.ETHEREALBLOOM.2=这种花只能净化沐浴在它荣光之下的8格范围内的土地.
#
tc.research_name.PECH=岩精
tc.research_text.PECH=古怪的生物
tc.research_page.PECH.1=这些奇怪的类人生物生活在位面间隙的薄层之中.它们被魔力所吸引,在魔力浓郁之处遍地皆是.<BR>不要被它们小小的个头愚弄了,实际上它们拥有不可思议的力气,能够携运数倍于自身重量的物品.<BR>岩精通常不具有主动攻击性.但一旦被激怒,就会成群结队地追杀攻击它们的人.一般情况下,尽可能不要招惹它们.<BR>岩精是出了名的吝啬鬼,尽管它们收藏了许多贵重物品,
tc.research_page.PECH.2=可杀死它们不会得到任何战利品.据说如果你为它们提供想要的材料就有可能能够与它们结交.成为朋友后它们常常会搬来一些它们不想要了的神奇物品给你.<BR>应当说明的一点是,这样的友谊很少能长久维持.<BR><IMG>thaumcraft:textures/research/research5.png:128:136:112:120:.75</IMG>
#
tc.research_name.INFUSIONENCHANTMENT=注魔法附魔
tc.research_text.INFUSIONENCHANTMENT=用要素源质附魔
tc.research_page.INFUSIONENCHANTMENT.1=悠悠数载岁月以降,巫师和神秘使已经将自己的生命能量灌注进物品来制造附魔武器,工具以及装备.而此种附魔方法过程单调乏味,结果难以预知.你关于注魔合成的研究揭露了解决这些问题的新方法.<BR>你对如何使用注魔坛对物品附魔已经了然于心.只需将你希望附魔的物品放置在中央的基座上,并提高合适的材料以及源质即可.
tc.research_page.INFUSIONENCHANTMENT.2=这种附魔同样需要提供经验形式的生命源质,但需求量远低于普通附魔所需.这些经验将从注魔坛附近的任意玩家身上抽取,因此使用时需要当心.<BR>I级附魔所消耗的源质和经验在如下配方中列出.若想对物品进行更高级别的附魔,只需重复进行注魔过程即可 - 该过程可重复进行直到所进行的附魔达到可能的最高等级.根据附魔等级不同,所消耗的源质和经验也将会有所不同,就比方说II级附魔将消耗I级附魔两倍的资源.
tc.research_page.INFUSIONENCHANTMENT.3=如若物品已包含你当前进行附魔类型外的附魔,可能会需要更多的消耗.每一级其他的附魔将会使得当前进行的附魔多消耗10%.例如,对一把亡灵杀手III的剑进行火焰附加I附魔,会额外消耗30%的源质和经验.<BR>随着物品上附魔增加注魔的风险也会增加.<BR>使用注魔坛附魔同样遵循一般物品附魔的搭配组合规律 - 附魔只能对特定类型物品进行.
#
tc.research_name.ARCANELAMP=奥术灯
tc.research_text.ARCANELAMP=大型光源
tc.research_page.ARCANELAMP.1=This mystical lamp can be attached to walls, floors or ceilings and will provide strong and steady light.<BR>Additional sources of light may also appear up to 16 blocks away wherever light levels fall below accepted 'safe' levels. Remember: Only YOU can prevent zombie outbreaks.<BR>These secondary sources of light will disappear soon after the lamp has been removed.<BR>The lamp can be turned off by applying a redstone signal.
tc.research_page.ARCANELAMP.2=§nArcane Bore§r<BR>When attached to the base of an arcane bore, the arcane lamp gains an additional ability: It will light up the tunnel that the bore digs.
#
tc.research_name.BASICARTIFACE=基础炼化学
tc.research_text.BASICARTIFACE=必需之物
tc.research_page.BASICARTIFACE.1=§n元始符咒§r<BR><BR>元始符咒是构筑许多神秘学构造的基础材料.出去能够汇聚和引导元始要素和源质外它们本身并无固有的能量.<BR>坊间相传这些符咒还有其他的能力,但那不过是些道听途说.
#
tc.research_name.TUBES=要素源质管道
tc.research_text.TUBES=运输要素源质
tc.research_page.TUBES.1=你已发现了好些运输要素源质的方法,但都被证明难以与大规模的炼金操作相适应 - 现在这问题解决了.<BR>你已破解了制作稳定及相对密封的管道的关键所在.尽管普通的化学物质可以用玻璃管道运输,但某些类型的要素源质却可能溶解掉或者直接穿透玻璃.在玻璃管道上裹上铁皮并用水银处理,让即使最不稳定的源质也能安全通过.黄金的管道配件装饰得管道系统极其美观.
tc.research_page.TUBES.2=管道可以与各种类型的奥法设备相连,尽管一般你主要用它连接要素罐子和蒸馏器.<BR>要素源质会主动流向任意可以容纳它的容器 - 比方说要素罐子.<BR>装有不同源质的罐子只会吸引那些同类要素源质.但管道一次只能吸入并运输一种类型的源质 - 吸力最高的会优先处理.若无法恰当使用阀门很容易导致管道系统堵塞.阀门的使用尤为关键.<LINE>
tc.research_page.TUBES.3=要素阀门类似一段普通管道,但可以通过手动或者红石信号控制其开闭.关闭阀门后通过它的源质流会被阻断.<LINE>要素谐振器是为管道系统排障的方便工具.你可以使用它查看管道或其他使用源质的设备中当前容纳着何种源质以及它们的吸力强弱.
tc.research_page.TUBES.4=Tubes can be connected and disconnected from their neighbors by clicking on a section of tubing with a wand.<BR>The wand can also be used to click on the central section to rotate certain tubes like the valve.
#
tc.research_name.CENTRIFUGE=奥法离心机
tc.research_text.CENTRIFUGE=分离物品
tc.research_page.CENTRIFUGE.1=奥法离心机是一种惊艳的能够将符合要素分解为更基本的前置要素的炼金设备<BR>当复合要素的源质从下方流入离心机,就会被慢慢分解成组成它们的前置的复合要素或元始要素.但每消耗一点源质只能得到一点前置要素.<BR>分离得到的要素源质需要从离心机顶部抽走.由于管道压力系统的特性,最好在离心机顶部连接一个§5要素缓冲器§0(见下页).
#
tc.research_name.TRAVELTRUNK=箱子宝宝
tc.research_text.TRAVELTRUNK=会走路的行李
tc.research_page.TRAVELTRUNK.1=这是一项对所有四处奔忙的神秘使来说都非常有用的傀儡学研究衍生产品:箱子宝宝.<BR>这个木头做的箱子会开开心心,蹦蹦跳跳跟在主人身后,充当一个便携的储物空间,装下你拾取的任意物品.<BR>箱子宝宝做得非常结实坚韧,能够承受大量的攻击,而且不畏火焰,也不会受到掉落伤害.<BR>箱子宝宝将追随它的主人前往任何地方——哪怕是跨位面的旅行.
tc.research_page.TRAVELTRUNK.2=但是如果你希望它不再跟着你,在它的界面里也有个很方便的按钮来让它留在原地.<BR>随着时间流逝箱子宝宝能够自己回复它受到的伤害,但你也可以喂给它任意食物来加快这个过程.<BR>用傀儡使铃铛能够像回收傀儡那样回收箱子宝宝.但这样做会让箱子宝宝装着的所有物品掉落在地上.按住潜行点击它会取下安装在它身上的升级,但有一定几率遗失.<BR>像普通的傀儡那样箱子宝宝能安装升级,但升级将对箱子宝宝起到独特的效果.如果你已经发现了相关升级可以阅读后面几页来查看详细信息.
tc.research_page.TRAVELTRUNK.UAI=§nGolem Upgrade: Air§r<BR>With this upgrade installed the traveling trunk will move faster.
tc.research_page.TRAVELTRUNK.UEA=§nGolem Upgrade: Earth§r<BR>With this upgrade installed the traveling trunk be able to carry more items and will gain an additional row in its inventory.
tc.research_page.TRAVELTRUNK.UFI=§nGolem Upgrade: Fire§r<BR>With this upgrade installed the traveling trunk will defend its master when he is attacked.
tc.research_page.TRAVELTRUNK.UWA=§nGolem Upgrade: Water§r<BR>With this upgrade installed the traveling trunk cannot be opened or picked up by anyone else but its master.<BR>It also become highly resistant to all but the most devastating amounts of damage.
tc.research_page.TRAVELTRUNK.UOR=§nGolem Upgrade: Order§r<BR>With this upgrade installed the traveling trunk will retain its items when it is picked up using a golemancer's bell. It will drop items as normal when shift-clicked is used.
tc.research_page.TRAVELTRUNK.UEN=§nGolem Upgrade: Entropy§r<BR>With this upgrade installed the traveling trunk will automatically suck in any nearby items it has room for.
#
tc.research_name.LAMPGROWTH=催生灯
tc.research_text.LAMPGROWTH=催熟作物
tc.research_page.LAMPGROWTH.1=不像奥术灯具就是用来照明的,除非提供Herba要素,催生灯不会散发出一丝光芒.而沐浴在其光芒之下的作物会生长得比平时更为快速.<BR>要素可以通过直接将灯具安装在源质管道上来提供.<BR>The lamp can be turned off by applying a redstone signal.
#
tc.research_name.LAMPFERTILITY=育种灯
tc.research_text.LAMPFERTILITY=散发出罗曼蒂克的光辉照耀事物
tc.research_page.LAMPFERTILITY.1=沐浴在此灯柔和的粉色光芒之中的所有动物都会径直陷入到更加罗曼蒂克的情绪之中.它们会尽可能地寻找同类交配.<BR>若某种动物已经达到8只或以上,这种灯便不会再对其造成影响.<BR>它需要victus要素来驱动.既可以将要素罐子放于附近,又可以直接将育种灯安附在要素源质管道系统中.<BR>The lamp can be turned off by applying a redstone signal.
#
tc.research_name.JARVOID=虚空罐子
tc.research_text.JARVOID=源质太多?这不可能!
tc.research_page.JARVOID.1=Void jars function much the same as normal warded jars with one important difference - even when full they are still able to accept essentia, but the excess essentia is simply vented as flux. This allows you to always have some essentia of that type available, but get rid of any excess that may build up.<BR>Like normal jars, void jars can accept labels, but their suction with a label is less than that of a normal labeled jar (about halfway between unlabeled and labeled jar).
#
tc.research_name.TUBEFILTER=高级源质管道
tc.research_text.TUBEFILTER=你需要什么,需要用它干什么
tc.research_page.TUBEFILTER.1=§nFiltered essentia tubes§r work like normal tubes, except it is possible to mark them with labels, phails or other items that clearly identify a single type of essentia. When marked they will restrict essentia flow through them to what they have been marked with.<BR>Shift-clicking on them with an empty hand will remove the filter.
tc.research_page.TUBEFILTER.2=§n限定源质管道§r 类似普通管道,但它们会将通过的源质吸力减半.<LINE>§n定向源质管道§r 只接受某个方向上抽取来的源质,蓝色标记指示了它接受抽取物的方向.
tc.research_page.TUBEFILTER.3=源质缓冲器能够允许你暂存一定量的源质 - 总计8点,可以是不同源质类型的任意组合.类似罐子它会自动吸收源质,但其吸力是各种可能中最小的(吸收的优先级最低).<BR>换言之通常只有在直接将其安附在源质来源处它才能吸入源质.然而管道可以连接在它所有的方向上,这意味着用它来提取像奥法离心机这种内置大量容纳空间的设备中的源质意义甚微.<BR>你可以为缓冲器安装奥术风箱 - 一个风箱提升64点吸力.
tc.research_page.TUBEFILTER.4=此外,类似普通的管道,你还能独立控制其每一方向连接的开合,但如若你按住shift点击连接,就能塞住它将其该方向上的吸力抑制在1(蓝圈)或者0(红圈).<BR>这使要素源质运输过程中的许多有趣特性有了可能.
#
tc.research_name.MIRRORESSENTIA=源质之镜
tc.research_text.MIRRORESSENTIA=随处可用的源质
tc.research_page.MIRRORESSENTIA.1=魔力手镜对长途运输物品可谓实用,但相同的原理能否应用于源质系统呢?你觉得你已经研究出实现它的方法了.<BR>源质之镜,顾名思义,可以类似魔力手镜传输物品那样传输源质.然而也有几条重要的使用限制：<BR>你无法用管道将源质导入镜中 - 源质之镜只能从源头抽取源质运输到类似注魔矩阵这样的设备去.
tc.research_page.MIRRORESSENTIA.2=意即镜子允许这些设备通过镜子从源头抽取源质.<BR>远距离抽取像源质这么不稳定的东西并非毫无风险,有时会造成少量源质流失.<BR>Like item mirrors, these mirrors cause great stress to the magical aura and will generate flux. 
#
tc.research_name.BONEBOW=骨弓
tc.research_text.BONEBOW=石为矢兮棍为箭,嘴上威风视等闲....
tc.research_page.BONEBOW.1=你已发现一种以白骨制弓,并灌注以混沌魔力的新工艺.<BR>这样打造出的武器射击速度远胜普通的弓,且箭矢速度更快,威力更猛.
#
tc.research_name.PRIMALARROW=元始之矢
tc.research_text.PRIMALARROW=元素伤害之箭矢
tc.research_page.PRIMALARROW.1=这些箭矢每种都灌注了特定类型的元始魔力,这赋予它们一些有趣而有破坏力的特性.<BR>§n风之矢§r<BR>缠绕在箭矢上的魔力劈啪作响.它们造成的伤害与普通箭矢类似,但魔力使得它们能够穿透任意类似的护甲.<BR>§n火之矢§r<BR>这种箭矢会造成纯粹的火焰伤害并点燃它们射中的目标.
tc.research_page.PRIMALARROW.2=§n水之矢§r<BR>这种箭矢造成的伤害与普通箭矢类似,但其附带的冰霜魔力会让你的目标寒至骨髓,从而减缓他们的移动速度.<BR>§n地之矢§r<BR>这种箭矢除去威力相比普通箭矢猛烈得多外,并无其他特殊属性.<BR>§n秩序矢§r<BR>这种箭矢威力略逊于普通箭矢,但它能穿刺护甲,且让你的敌人陷入虚弱.<BR>§n混沌矢§r<BR>这种箭矢威力略逊于普通箭矢,
tc.research_page.PRIMALARROW.3=但无论射中什么都会造成凋灵效果.<LINE>元始之矢无法从地上拾起来,且即使是无限附魔也只有1/3的几率可以减免元始之矢的消耗.
#
tc.research_name.THAUMATORIUM=自动炼金
tc.research_text.THAUMATORIUM=大众炼金学
tc.research_page.THAUMATORIUM.1=迄今炼金术多少有些变成一件撞运道的差事 - 误算数量的要素,品质低劣的源质和炼金配料全都需要手动劳作去混合.这些总算成为了过去.<BR>神秘炼金塔真是了不起的发明！它使得神秘使者能够选择使用何种配方,添加何种催化剂.它还能够使用管道自动从可用的源头抽取源质.只要尚还提供有催化剂它就能够一直完美地产出所需的物品.<BR>这种坩埚并不需要添水,但下方依然需要提供热源.
tc.research_page.THAUMATORIUM.2=当你开启该设备会看见一些格子.左上方的格子用来放置催化剂.添置好后在右上格子中便可以从该种催化剂能够参与的所有可能配方中选择你想要合成的那个.<BR>下方的长条会按所需顺序显示所需的源质.当设备运作时它还会显示进度条.<BR>制成的物品会从设备前方弹出,或者进入到放置在弹射口位置的容器中.
tc.research_page.THAUMATORIUM.3=一般来说一个炼金塔只能同时激活一个配方,但在其周围安附记忆矩阵就能增加它同时监控的配方数量.<BR>每个记忆矩阵能够增添2个配方.
#
tc.research_name.RUNICARMOR=符文护盾
tc.research_text.RUNICARMOR=护盾开启!
tc.research_page.RUNICARMOR.1=对防护法术的研究最终使你发明出符文护盾.它并非传统意义上的护甲装备,而是一种佩戴在日常衣物上的符咒,纹章或类似防护物品.<BR>这种物品会制造出一个防范绝大多数伤害的魔力屏障.护盾会拥有一个伤害量承受池来先一步减免损伤,以保护佩戴者免受各种伤害.当伤害量承受池耗尽佩戴者才会开始像平常一样承受伤害.<BR>伤害量承受池随着时间推移会自己回复,但即使是耗尽状态也至少会为佩戴者提供基本上相当于皮革装备的防护.
tc.research_page.RUNICARMOR.2=The pool replenishes over time and requires §2Terra§0 and §eAer§0 vis to replenish its charge which it draws from the aura.<BR>The armor offers no protection from damage suffered due to drowning, starvation or similar environmental hazards.<BR>Due to its nature the armor cannot be enchanted by normal means, but you are sure there are ways to improve its effectiveness - you just need to discover them.
#
tc.research_name.RUNICAUGMENTATION=增广符文护盾
tc.research_text.RUNICAUGMENTATION=护盾全开
tc.research_page.RUNICAUGMENTATION.1=嵌有符文护盾的指环,护身符,腰带都非常好用,但你是否确定能将这只防护附魔应用于其他物品呢？<BR>当然你可以的！利用神秘学法术(c) (专利申请中),你将能够将符文护盾镶入多数魔力稳定的装备.<BR>魔力稳定的装备指用神秘锭,魔力布匹或相似魔法材料制成的那些.<BR>只有单次充能的符文护盾能够镶嵌到物品上,但你可以对其进行多次附魔.
tc.research_page.RUNICAUGMENTATION.2=然而这非常昂贵,消耗的源质量会随级别而上升.需求的世界盐同防护级别成正比,耗费的源质则指数级增加.你也可以对像护盾戒指这样已经做好的符文物品附魔,然而其源质消耗会基于已存在的符文蓄能来计算,这会使得该过程的消耗异常昂贵.
#
tc.research_name.RUNICSPECIAL=Specialized Runic Baubles
tc.research_text.RUNICSPECIAL=Charge for the Charge Ring!
tc.research_page.RUNICSPECIAL.1=§nCharged Ring of Shielding§r<BR>This is a specialized version of the Ring of Shielding.<BR>It has slightly less charge than the ring it is based on, but increases the recharge time of runic shielding by 25%.<BR>You can wear more than one of these rings, effectively halving the normal recharge time.
tc.research_page.RUNICSPECIAL.2=§nRevitalizing Ring of Shielding§r<BR>This is a specialized version of the Ring of Shielding.<BR>It has slightly less charge than the ring it is based on, but when your runic shielding is breached it will release a pulse of regenerative energy that will last for a few seconds.<BR>This effect cannot trigger more than once every 20 seconds.
tc.research_page.RUNICSPECIAL.3=§nKinetic Girdle of Shielding§r<BR>This is a specialized version of the Girdle of Shielding.<BR>It has slightly less charge than the girdle it is based on, but when your shielding is breached a detonation of kinetic energy will be released damaging and shoving back anything nearby.<BR>This effect cannot trigger more than once every 20 seconds.
tc.research_page.RUNICSPECIAL.4= §nAmulet of Emergency Shielding§r<BR>This is a specialized version of the Amulet of Shielding.<BR>It has slightly less charge than the amulet it is based on, but when your shielding is breached this upgrade will instantly add 8 charge to your shielding amount.<BR>This effect cannot trigger more than once a minute.
#
tc.research_name.WARDEDARCANA=守护之奥术
tc.research_text.WARDEDARCANA=门禁控制
tc.research_page.WARDEDARCANA.1=一些实验产生了某个有趣的发现 - 即向没有生命的物品印刻记忆的技术.应用这项知识,你首先尝试着制造出能记住放置者的奥能之扉,奥术压力盘和守卫者方块.<BR>奥能之扉只能由放置者通过法杖移除.此外它默认会拒绝对主人外的任何人敞开.其主人可以通过配制铁钥匙或者金钥匙来分享进门的权限.<BR>合成出铁钥匙并拿着它点击奥能之扉,便能够将钥匙与门配对.
tc.research_page.WARDEDARCANA.2=你可以将铁钥匙交给其他人,当他们对这扇门使用钥匙后便可以获得进门的永久权限.但他们并不能破坏这扇门,也无法向其他人分享进门权限.除非你制作一柄金钥匙.<BR>金钥匙大部分功能与铁钥匙类似,但使用它的其他人还会获得向其他玩家分享铁钥匙的权限.只有门的最初拥有者才有权限制作金钥匙.使用金钥匙的人也无法用法杖拆掉奥能之门,那也是最初拥有者的特权.
tc.research_page.WARDEDARCANA.3=奥术压力盘有一些新奇的特性.<BR>首先通过右键点击可以切换它的三种设定: (像木质压力盘一样)什么都能触发它的模式,仅仅只有主人触发的模式,以及除了主人外均可以触发的模式.<BR>其次,类似其他守卫者系列的物品,只有主人才能移除它.<BR>最后,它也能够通过钥匙绑定到其他玩家身上.这些压力盘能够用来开启奥能之扉,只要踩上压力盘的人本身也有进入这扇门的权限.
tc.research_page.WARDEDARCANA.4=守卫者玻璃并非单纯的装饰方块,类似其他守卫者系列物品,它也无法被放置者外的人破坏.<BR>亦无法用钥匙向他人分享破坏它的权限.
#
tc.research_name.VISAMULET=魔力存储
tc.research_text.VISAMULET=俭以防匮
tc.research_page.VISAMULET.1=Most of the time a single wand is more than enough for any thaumaturge, but there are occasions that the vis it stores just isn't enough. Carrying more than one wand would solve this, but experimentation has shown that there is another way.<BR>By crafting an amulet capable of storing vis, you will be able to recharge wands and other items in the field while it is being worn.<BR>Your success has been mixed however. You can only recharge wands while holding them in your hand and even then the recharge rate is slow. 
tc.research_page.VISAMULET.2=However the amulet is able to act as a good power source for other things like the Repair enchant or runic shielding.<BR>The amulet recharges itself slowly while worn, or it can be placed in a recharge pedestal.
#
tc.research_name.GOLEMFETTER=傀儡脚镣
tc.research_text.GOLEMFETTER=教他们守规矩
tc.research_page.GOLEMFETTER.1=这台小设备能够帮助傀儡师让他们的傀儡暂时停下脚步.<BR>当任何傀儡经过用红石信号激活后的傀儡脚镣时,会完全立定,中断当前进行的任务.<BR>当设备被关闭时傀儡会继续动起来做未完成的工作.
#
tc.research_name.WORKBENCHCHARGER=Arcane Workbench Charger
tc.research_text.WORKBENCHCHARGER=Arcane Crafting Simplified
tc.research_page.WORKBENCHCHARGER.1=An annoyance for any thaumaturge that performs regular arcane crafting is to constantly keep his wand charged.<BR>Now that you have found an automated way to draw vis directly from the auran you are able to craft an Arcane Workbench Charger. It is designed to be placed on top of an arcane crafting table and will draw vis from the aura to recharge wands placed in the table.<BR>The only drawback is that it recharges much slower than it would from a wand recharging pedestal or doing it by hand. 
#
tc.research_name.WARP=扭曲,咒波,所有那些坏东西
tc.research_text.WARP=万物都有其价值所在
tc.research_page.WARP.1= §n扭曲§r<BR>许多人认为人类不应当涉足魔法的领域,再没有什么比扭曲的存在更能支持这种观点了.<BR>从事禁忌的魔法研究或者制作那些有悖于自然的造物,都会让神秘使眼中的现实世界无论在精神上还是在肉体上都出现畸变.此种效果谓之扭曲.<BR>目前尚未有摆脱这种效果的方法,一旦选择不顾危险地追逐力量的神秘使身上出现扭曲现象,境况就会犹如滑坡效应般每况愈下.
tc.research_page.WARP.2=扭曲通常表现为心神恍惚,肉体疼痛或者出现幻觉.<BR>这些症状并不仅仅只是精神疾患,有时候视野中会涌现出有用的知识,而幻觉看上去骇人地真实.
tc.research_page.WARP.3=§n咒波§r<BR>倘若说扭曲是魔力紊乱在精神上的表现,那么咒波就是其物理上的表现.<BR>咒波能够以三种形式表现出来:液态,气态,以及身体疾患的状态.前两种是令大多数神秘使都烦恼过的问题,它们通常是魔力滥用的后果,并不特别难以清除,但它们常常会导致第三种形式出现: 以身体疾患为表现的咒流.<BR>咒流并不特别危险,但一旦神秘使染上这种疾病,聚集魔力就会变得更加困难,导致他不得不得在同样的操作中耗费更多魔力.
#
tc.research_name.BATHSALTS=净化浴盐
tc.research_text.BATHSALTS=缓解精神压力
tc.research_page.BATHSALTS.1=扭曲即使对那些最谨慎的神秘使来说都很危险.那些身染数种扭曲的神秘使更是不胜其烦.而净化浴盐有助于解决他们的问题.<BR>只需要将这些盐分溶解在水中,就能将水变为银光闪闪的净化之水,用它进行沐浴,能够舒缓日间的疲惫,暂时祛除扭曲的效果.需要注意的是,神秘使所患扭曲疾病愈甚,沐浴净化之水所产生的保护效果持续时间就愈短暂.<BR>这些浴盐难以保存,如若随意放置极容易溶解.
#
tc.research_name.LIQUIDDEATH=死亡之水
tc.research_text.LIQUIDDEATH=仅限外敷
tc.research_page.LIQUIDDEATH.1=这种液体是一直极其危险的试剂,销肉融骨,甚至能融化更坚固的物质.没有任何生命或者表现为生命的东西能够与之共存.<BR>除去非常明显的应用外,这种邪恶的物质还拥有一种奇妙的特性: 被消融的生物种蕴含的源质会以可采集的水晶的形式留存下来.<BR>至于这些水晶究竟有何妙用就有待读者自己大开脑洞了.
#
tc.research_name.ARMORFORTRESS=神秘要塞甲胄
tc.research_text.ARMORFORTRESS=百害莫侵
tc.research_page.ARMORFORTRESS.1=神秘要塞甲胄优点虽多,但基础的构材等级却逊于钻石护甲.在提升其构材性能以及复杂性的同时,你逐渐发展出一门额外提升护甲的工艺,耐久和强度的技术.<BR>每个独立的神秘要塞甲胄部件都有和钻石护甲同等程度的防护能力,不仅如此,它们还具有更加卓绝的耐久值,并且对火焰和魔法伤害有特别的额外防护效果.<BR>但它们最不可思议的奇妙之处在于独立的护甲部件如果同时穿戴将会激活套装效果:
tc.research_page.ARMORFORTRESS.2=每多穿戴一件部件,都会提升其他部件的防护效果,外观造型也会变得更加炫酷.<BR>由于构材中使用的大量神秘锭,这种护甲很容易附魔.
#
tc.research_name.HELMGOGGLES=揭示之盔
tc.research_text.HELMGOGGLES=神秘要塞兜鍪改装
tc.research_page.HELMGOGGLES.1=通常来说,神秘使需要在防护性与实用性间艰难地做出选择.再也不必如此了.!<BR>这顶改装后的神秘要塞兜鍪虽然并不具有护目镜的魔力减免功能,但却能够为你提供揭示之护目镜所具有的其他所有功能.<BR>这顶头盔也能加装面具.
#
tc.research_name.MASKGRINNINGDEVIL=狞笑恶魔面具
tc.research_text.MASKGRINNINGDEVIL=神秘要塞兜鍪升级
tc.research_page.MASKGRINNINGDEVIL.1=此面具乃是神秘要塞兜鍪的专属附件.<BR>戴上这幅面具会获得奇妙的阻滞扭曲效果的能力.虽说无法阻止扭曲发生,但却能够让它的效果一定程度上被削弱.<BR>看来笑对人生之峥嵘,的确能够有所收获.
#
tc.research_name.MASKANGRYGHOST=暴怒幽魂面具
tc.research_text.MASKANGRYGHOST=神秘要塞兜鍪升级
tc.research_page.MASKANGRYGHOST.1=此面具乃是神秘要塞兜鍪的专属附件.<BR>当身处战场,那些攻击戴上这幅冷酷面具后的你的生物,都会有一定几率染上凋灵效果.<BR>真是自己作死!
#
tc.research_name.MASKSIPPINGFIEND=嗜血邪妖面具
tc.research_text.MASKSIPPINGFIEND=神秘要塞兜鍪升级
tc.research_page.MASKSIPPINGFIEND.1=此面具乃是神秘要塞兜鍪的专属附件.<BR>戴上这幅面具后的你如果攻击其他生物,有时候会窃取它们的生命力用来强化自己.<BR>你吸它们血的事情实际上似乎并没有像你以为那样让你觉得有什么异样.但你疑惑的是你该不该对此忧心呢?
#
tc.research_name.ELDRITCHMINOR=邪术揭谛
tc.research_text.ELDRITCHMINOR=迈入未知的第一步
tc.research_page.ELDRITCHMINOR.1=突然间对你来说它变得昭然若揭.在其他人仅能看见混沌一片的地方,你却灵光一瞥地捕捉到它那诡异莫名,令人不安的模式.宇宙最黑暗的角落鬼影绰绰.<BR>你一度试图向别人解释你发现的一切,但却只招来了古怪的眼神.无论如何,有朝一日你终将向他们展示你的发现.<BR>向他们所有人.
#
tc.research_name.ELDRITCHMAJOR=邪术启示录
tc.research_text.ELDRITCHMAJOR=吾已看见那超越无限疆域的妙境
tc.research_page.ELDRITCHMAJOR.1=神秘的面纱已滑落 - 吾脑中敞开了众妙之门.<BR>吾抬眼所见尽是奇迹之景.不,并非奇迹,§m吾所见者,乃是§r<BR>§o吾所见者……吾所见者……所见者……所见乃是……§r<IMG>thaumcraft:textures/misc/eldritchajor1.png:0:255:255:255:.5</IMG>
tc.research_page.ELDRITCHMAJOR.2=<IMG>thaumcraft:textures/misc/eldritchajor2.png:0:255:255:255:.5</IMG><BR><BR>这条谁写的啊喂?
#
tc.research_name.VOIDMETAL=虚空金属
tc.research_text.VOIDMETAL=奇怪,它摸起来应该是凉的...
tc.research_page.VOIDMETAL.1=通过向金属灌入魔力你曾制造出神秘锭,还算是了不得的发现吧,不过今后就把它们留给那些浅尝辄止的业余爱好人士吧.<BR>那依稀能回想起内容的怪诞梦境让你产生了去尝试一些更加与众不同的事物的冲动.假如你向金属灌入的并非魔力,而是那些产生魔力的源泉,那些存在于群星之间的黑暗和虚空要素,又会怎样呢?<BR>如此所得的金属摸起来令人不安地光滑而温暖.它软如黄金,因此易于加工,但一旦被加工成型,便会变得犹如神秘锭一般坚硬,有时甚至犹有过之.
tc.research_page.VOIDMETAL.2=令人印象更加深刻的是,哪怕是毁灭性的损坏它也能够很快地自动复原,金属会自动流向它原本所在的位置.<BR>唯一的劣势是它不再像神秘锭那样易被附魔,但即使如此它的附魔性能也胜过铁这样的世俗材料.<BR>使用这种金属时你发现有一点必须加以关注 - 被它伤害到似乎会暂时性地陷入疲弱无力的状态.
#
tc.research_name.ARMORVOIDFORTRESS=虚空神秘使法袍
tc.research_text.ARMORVOIDFORTRESS=外域风情
tc.research_page.ARMORVOIDFORTRESS.1=一位真正有所领悟的神秘使能够认识到他不必一定要在实用性和防护能力间做出选择.<BR>通过合适的附魔手段增幅虚空护甲,并将它们与神秘使法袍相结合做成的防护套装,不仅能够提供物理防护,辅助凝神施咒,还能提供魔法防护.<BR>鉴于兜帽在制造时使用了护目镜因而保留了其全部能力,所以这套法袍也具有虚空护甲的全部特性.<BR>这套法袍能够被染色.
#
tc.research_name.ARCANESPA=奥术浴场
tc.research_text.ARCANESPA=时髦的休闲方式
tc.research_page.ARCANESPA.1=手动将浴盐洒进水里略显琐碎无聊,好在神秘使能够通过一点点魔法手段轻松地解决这个问题.<BR>你已制造出一台便捷的设备,能够自动混合水和浴盐,并将它们泵出到设备上方的空间.泵出的流体将填满机器正上方5X5大小的区域.<BR>另外,你发现它也能用于将任意其他流体泵出.你可以使用自动化设备装填它,或者拿着合适的容器右击方块.通入红石信号能够关闭它. 
#
tc.research_name.SANESOAP=祛邪肥皂
tc.research_text.SANESOAP=摆脱那些肮脏的念头吧
tc.research_page.SANESOAP.1=净化肉体固然容易,但一旦陷入扭曲之苦,就同样需要洗涤心灵的妙法.<BR>这块肥皂能够清洗肉体上的污垢,但它真正特别之处在于还能对你的精神世界产生效果.它能够祛除所有暂时性的扭曲,并有小几率能够祛除非永久性的扭曲.<BR>浸泡净化之水或处于扭曲守护状态时使用这块肥皂能够增加它生效的几率.
#
tc.research_name.SANITYCHECK=神智检测仪
tc.research_text.SANITYCHECK=勇敢者的内省
tc.research_page.SANITYCHECK.1=近来你的脑海中一片纷繁.似乎你应当好好内省一番,以确保没有哪里不对劲.<BR>神智检测仪能够帮助你查看精神世界的扭曲效果以及它们会如何影响你.<BR>理所当然地,你不可能允许这些资料落入敌手,因此你煞费苦心地让它提供的信息模糊而晦涩.不过你似乎做得过头了 - 你自己理解起来都有点困难.
#
tc.research_name.CRIMSON=血腥崇拜
tc.research_text.CRIMSON=一部警示录
tc.research_page.CRIMSON.1=书册内容多以密如蛛网,不知所云的字符写成,但你明确读懂的部分让你对那些血腥邪徒的目的隐隐约约有了奇怪的了解.<BR>它们的起源之因仍笼罩在谜雾中,但似乎它们正致力于完成一种被它们称为"Apertis Oculis"的开眼仪式.这仪式究竟是做什么的尚不清楚,但你怀疑那并不是什么好事.<BR>蛮有趣的是,你认为你的神秘学知识恰好能够补完它们长久以来一直在寻找的仪式所残缺的部分.很明显开展这类研究纯属疯子行径...
#
tc.research_name.OCULUS=开眼仪式
tc.research_text.OCULUS=向他们展示你的发现,向他们所有人.
tc.research_page.OCULUS.1=It was all so simple - you are amazed the Crimson Cultists have never discovered this.<BR>To perform the ritual you simply need to place four Eldritch Eyes on the specially marked keystone found at one of the strange altars where you first discovered the cult.<BR>Once this is done it is a simple matter of infusing a large amount of primal vis into the keystone with a wand - 1000 units of each should be sufficient.
tc.research_page.OCULUS.2=如果所有步骤均正确,那么仪式将被完成而名为"眼"之存在将会睁开.<BR>当然你并不知道那意味着什么.不过那又有什么关系呢?只有傻瓜才会畏惧未知.
#
tc.research_name.ESSENTIARESERVOIR=高级源质存储
tc.research_text.ESSENTIARESERVOIR=别磕着它
tc.research_page.ESSENTIARESERVOIR.1=多数类型的源质相当容易挥发,需要小心储存 - 这也是普通神秘使会选择使用密闭罐子的原因所在.可是你并非那些普通的神秘使.<BR>通过使用一种名为虚空锭的神奇新物质,你发现一种显著提升源质存储能力的方法.源质库能够容纳256点任意类型组合的源质.<BR>这种新型金属构筑的动态隔间都够有效隔绝不同类型的源质从而弥除异种源质混合可能会造成的潜在危险.
tc.research_page.ESSENTIARESERVOIR.2=类似罐子,源质库也只有一面能够参与源质物流系统,尽管你可以指定这一面的朝向.不幸的是,这种容器无法手动清空或者手动填装,你必须借助于傀儡或者源质管道.<BR>不推荐挖掉盛有内容的源质库.<BR>这项发现让你喜悦万分,因此你向一些神秘使伙伴展示了它.奇怪的是,他们多数都一副避之不及的样子,即使你已经向他们保证经过极端高压处理后这种金属的安全性值得信任.
#
tc.research_name.ESSENTIACRYSTAL=源质结晶器 
tc.research_text.ESSENTIACRYSTAL=要硬通货,还是要流动资产?
tc.research_page.ESSENTIACRYSTAL.1=You have nearly mastered the art of turning concrete objects into liquid essentia, so doing the reverse is a simple matter.<BR>The essentia crystallizer draws in liquid essentia from a pipe network and converts it into small shards of crystalline essentia. Crystalline essentia is safe to handle and very stable.<BR>The Crystallizer either ejects the crystals into the world or into a container. It can be disabled with a redstone signal.<BR>It draws terra vis from the aura to power itself.
#
tc.research_name.BANNERS=旗帜
tc.research_text.BANNERS=警告:仅用于装饰
tc.research_page.BANNERS.1=有时候,神秘使也不并需要创造出那些撼动现实根基的东西,他们只不过想做出一些赏心悦目的装饰品.<BR>你发明出一种能够在旗帜上描绘神秘学符文的便捷附魔方法.只需要拿着要素安瓿点击旗帜就能将相应的符文镌写在旗面上.按住shift右击则可以擦除旗帜上的符文图案.
#
tc.research_name.BOTTLETAINT=腐化瓶
tc.research_text.BOTTLETAINT=为什么你会想要这个?
tc.research_page.BOTTLETAINT.1=清除腐化自然是一回事,可若想传播它呢?<BR>将腐化源质浓缩并收集到瓶中,将其抛出就能将那里变成一小片腐化之地.至于你意欲何为就是你自己的事了.
#
tc.research_name.FOCALMANIPULATION=核心镶饰台
tc.research_text.FOCALMANIPULATION=重制法杖核心
tc.research_page.FOCALMANIPULATION.1=Wand foci are capable of amazing feats, but they aren't very flexible. A single focus is seldom capable of performing more than a single function.<BR>You have discovered a way to upgrade basic foci to alter the way they manipulate magic. You simply need to place a focus in a Focal Manipulator and choose the upgrade you wish to apply to it. It will draw vis from the aura and you also need to provide it with experience points to get the process started, but after that it is a simple matter of waiting.<BR>Each focus can be upgraded up to five times, 
tc.research_page.FOCALMANIPULATION.2=每次升级都会显著提高升级的消耗.<BR>有些升级可以进行多次,无需考虑顺序.而有些升级则要求按照特定序列进行,其中有些会要求已经进行过前置的升级.因此最好多加实验.<BR>升级是永久性的 - 你还未曾想到移除升级的方法,因此选择时切记走心.
#
tc.research_name.VAMPBAT=五阶升级:嗜血魔蝠
tc.research_text.VAMPBAT=恶毒的小吸血鬼们
#
tc.research_name.PRIMPEARL=元始珍珠
tc.research_text.PRIMPEARL=开端之前
tc.research_page.PRIMPEARL.1=平生头一回你发觉自己在面对一个你认为不可能被解决的问题.<BR>这玩意儿中蕴含着纯净的元始要素,但它们拥有的特性却与你所以为的普通寻常的元始要素截然不同.你对为何如此所知甚少:<BR>要么这种所谓的珍珠是现实世界创造伊始时残留的物质 - 最基础的魔法早在它们尚未融合形成更加复杂的要素时就已经存在.<BR>要么它可能是来自某个神奇的地方,
tc.research_page.PRIMPEARL.2=那里并不遵循你刚开始有所了解的已知魔法规则.你难以确定哪一种解释更让人担忧.<BR>无论如何,这种珍珠都是强大的魔法物品,蕴含巨大的魔力,拥有近乎无穷的潜能.<BR>是时候将其投诸实用了.
#
tc.research_name.PRIMNODE=元始节点操纵
tc.research_text.PRIMNODE=只是放一块摩擦摩擦，看看会否有奇妙火花
tc.research_page.PRIMNODE.1=你草创了一种值得深究的新理论.为何不试试将元始珍珠融入灵气节点中呢?<BR>当然,将两种原始魔力的源泉汇聚一处很可能造成灾难性的后果.但两者之交互亦可能会非常... 有趣.<BR>尽管无论这种实验谁都能完成,但你确信一旦这项研究完成将略微有所帮助.略略略微.
#
tc.research_name.FLUXSCRUB=咒波洗涤器
tc.research_text.FLUXSCRUB=混乱神秘使的福利
tc.research_page.FLUXSCRUB.1=即使是最富技巧的神秘使也难免因为咒波污染留下一大堆乱摊子,清理它们是所有人都必须面对的麻烦,但这台设备能够让你减轻这些折磨人的苦差.<BR>咒波洗涤器,当使用aer要素驱动后,将会缓慢地对所在位置16格半径内的各种类型的咒波加以清理.不仅如此,它还能够将部分咒波以praecantatio源质的形式回收.<BR>它内置的缓存空间很小,即使已经满了也会持续运作,因此,如果你希望回收掉所有的praecantatio源质,那么你就需要及时地将它清空.
#
tc.research_name.ENTEROUTER=外域
tc.research_text.ENTEROUTER=我有种感觉,这里已经不是堪萨斯了
tc.research_page.ENTEROUTER.1=通过开眼仪式时你并不十分确定你究竟在期待什么,但肯定不是眼前这些碎裂石块建成的诡异建筑和这些七拐八弯的扭曲通道.<BR>这里有些不对劲 - 这些建筑物看上去除了构成巨大的致命迷宫外别无设计目的.<BR>四周涌动着诡异的能量波动,你的魔力在这异域的环境中似乎表现得有些异常.即使你遇到的其他生物看上去也给你一种格格不入的诡异感觉.
#
tc.research_name.OUTERREV=外域之启示
tc.research_text.OUTERREV=事物并非如它们咋眼所见
tc.research_page.OUTERREV.1=你所疑虑的事情得到了证实.这里并非你打算命名为外域人的种族的家园.这完全是另一个地方.你并不相信它存在于你所理解的"现实"当中 - 相比实在的事物它更接近某种精神上的结构,但什么样的精神能够容纳它呢?<BR>你仅仅能破译出少量的符文,但你确信这地方是一个陷阱,一个用于考验来客并淘汰掉弱者的地方.出于何种目的你还不得而知.
#
tc.research_name.SINSTONE=凶险磁石
tc.research_text.SINSTONE=你敢跟来吗?
tc.research_page.SINSTONE.1=研究节点的过程中你有一个有趣的发现.不同类型的节点都会发出不同类型的辐射能量,但它们大都不像凶险节点那样独树一帜.<BR>凶险节点发出的能量十分独特且易于追踪.你认为利用向燧石注魔得到的简易探测设备就能够帮助你指明凶险节点所指向的地方.<BR>探测范围非常有限,但这项发明物有所值,因为你发现凶险节点通常会出现在那些最有趣的地方.
#
tc.research_name.PRIMALCRUSHER=元始杵
tc.research_text.PRIMALCRUSHER=破尽万物
tc.research_page.PRIMALCRUSHER.1=注魔合成背后的原理并不复杂 - 向一件物品中灌注要素源质以及其他物品的特性.这种工艺的效果尽管有其局限,但是,在发现元始珍珠后,这些局限似乎变得越来越少.<BR>你试图将完全不同的物品的特性注入珍珠的实验获得了惊人的成功.元始杵是这项发现结出的第一枚硕果.<BR>通过将后土铲,炽心镐的特性融入虚空金属你制成了一柄具备无可比拟的破坏能力的工具,
tc.research_page.PRIMALCRUSHER.2=它拥有组成部件大多数的能力.<BR>元始杵挖土掘石都视若等闲,并且能够一次作用于3X3的范围.类似炽心镐,它有时会挖出原矿簇而非天然的矿石.<BR>它能够随着时间推移恢复耐久,具有良好的附魔性,揍人打怪时也是不可多得的好武器.<BR>遗憾的是由于追求纯碎的破坏力,它似乎没能保留其原型所具有的建造和探测的能力.
#
tc.research_name.WATERJUG=Everfull Urn
tc.research_text.WATERJUG=A source of infinite water
tc.research_page.WATERJUG.1=A small fountain of pure water always flows from the top of this urn, making it a perfect water source to fill your buckets, bottles or other liquid containers.<BR>It will also automatically replenish any liquid containers within two blocks of it if they can accept water from the top. This is perfect for automatically refilling crucibles, but has other uses as well.<BR>Every bucket full of water created costs 1 §3Aqua§0 vis which is drawn from the aura.
#
